WEBVTT

00:00:11.060 --> 00:00:11.820
PREFACE.

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:22.500
This book is pragmatical, not philosophical.

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:25.760
Practical manual, not a treatise upon theories.

00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:33.240
It is intended for the men and women, whose most pressing need is for money, who wish to get rich first and philosophize afterward.

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:41.500
It is for those who have, so far, found neither the time, the means, nor the opportunity to go deeply into the study of metaphysics,

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:46.860
but who want results and who are willing to take the conclusions of science as a basis for action,

00:00:47.220 --> 00:00:51.240
without going into all the processes by which those conclusions were reached.

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:55.720
It is expected that the reader will take the fundamental statements upon faith,

00:00:55.960 --> 00:01:02.560
just as he would take statements concerning a law of electrical action if they were promulgated by a Marconi or an Edison,

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:09.900
and taking the statements upon faith that he will prove their truth by acting upon them without fear or hesitation.

00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:18.840
Every man or woman who does this will certainly get rich, for the science herein applied is an exact science, and failure is impossible.

00:01:19.480 --> 00:01:26.220
For the benefit, however, of those who wish to investigate philosophical theories and so secure a logical basis of faith,

00:01:26.620 --> 00:01:28.580
I will here cite certain authorities.

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:34.040
The monistic theory of the universe, the theory that one is all and that all is one,

00:01:34.580 --> 00:01:40.860
that one substance manifests itself as the seeming many elements of the material world, is of Hindu origin,

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:45.980
and has been gradually winning its way into the thought of the Western world for two hundred years.

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:54.460
It is the foundation of all the oriental philosophies and of those of Descartes, Spinoza, Leibniz, Schopenhauer, Hegel and Emerson.

00:01:55.080 --> 00:02:01.040
The reader who would dig the philosophical foundations of this is advised to read Hegel and Emerson for himself.

00:02:01.620 --> 00:02:08.680
In writing this book I have sacrificed all other considerations to plainness and simplicity of style, so that all might understand.

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:13.360
The plan of action laid down herein was deduced from the conclusions of philosophy.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:19.080
It has been thoroughly tested, and bears the supreme test of practical experiment. It works.

00:02:19.580 --> 00:02:24.600
If you wish to know how the conclusions were arrived at, read the writings of the authors mentioned above.

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:31.940
And if you wish to reap the fruits of their philosophies in actual practice, read this book and do exactly as it tells you to do.

00:02:53.612 --> 00:02:58.182
Whatever may be said in praise of poverty, the fact remains that it is not possible to

00:02:58.182 --> 00:03:01.302
live a really complete or successful life unless one is rich.

00:03:01.842 --> 00:03:07.242
No man can rise to his greatest possible height in talent or soul development unless he has

00:03:07.242 --> 00:03:11.922
plenty of money, for to unfold a soul and to develop talent he must have many things

00:03:11.922 --> 00:03:15.962
to use, and he cannot have these things unless he has money to buy them with.

00:03:16.642 --> 00:03:22.002
A man develops in mind, soul and body by making use of things, and society is so organized

00:03:22.002 --> 00:03:26.562
that man must have money in order to become the possessor of things, therefore the basis

00:03:26.562 --> 00:03:30.182
of all advancement for a man must be the science of getting rich.

00:03:30.822 --> 00:03:36.022
The object of all life is development, and everything that lives has an inalienable right

00:03:36.022 --> 00:03:38.522
to all the development it is capable of attaining.

00:03:39.182 --> 00:03:43.722
Man's right to life means his right to have the free and unrestricted use of all the things

00:03:43.722 --> 00:03:49.182
which may be necessary to his fullest mental, spiritual and physical unfoldment, or in other

00:03:49.182 --> 00:03:50.902
words his right to be rich.

00:03:51.662 --> 00:03:55.062
In this book I shall not speak of riches in a figurative way.

00:03:55.462 --> 00:03:59.082
To be really rich does not mean to be satisfied or contented with a little.

00:03:59.722 --> 00:04:04.162
No man ought to be satisfied with a little if he is capable of using and enjoying more.

00:04:04.162 --> 00:04:09.322
The purpose of nature is the advancement and unfoldment of life, and every man should have

00:04:09.322 --> 00:04:13.482
all that can contribute to the power, elegance, beauty and richness of life.

00:04:13.962 --> 00:04:16.042
To be content with less is sinful.

00:04:16.802 --> 00:04:21.422
The man who owns all he wants for the living of all the life he is capable of living is

00:04:21.422 --> 00:04:25.622
rich, and no man who has not plenty of money can have all he wants.

00:04:26.602 --> 00:04:32.602
Life has advanced so far and become so complex that even the most ordinary man or woman requires

00:04:32.602 --> 00:04:37.102
a great amount of wealth in order to live in a manner that even approaches completeness.

00:04:37.782 --> 00:04:41.322
Every person naturally wants to become all that they are capable of becoming.

00:04:41.742 --> 00:04:46.062
This desire to realize innate possibilities is inherent in human nature.

00:04:46.582 --> 00:04:49.122
We cannot help wanting to be all that we can be.

00:04:49.722 --> 00:04:52.022
Success in life is becoming what you want to be.

00:04:52.402 --> 00:04:56.702
You can become what you want to be only by making use of things, and you can have the

00:04:56.702 --> 00:04:59.902
free use of things only as you become rich enough to buy them.

00:04:59.902 --> 00:05:04.682
To understand the science of getting rich is therefore the most essential of all knowledge.

00:05:05.562 --> 00:05:07.822
There is nothing wrong in wanting to get rich.

00:05:08.402 --> 00:05:13.222
The desire for riches is really the desire for a richer, fuller and more abundant life,

00:05:13.322 --> 00:05:15.162
and that desire is praiseworthy.

00:05:15.962 --> 00:05:21.342
The man who does not desire to live more abundantly is abnormal, and so the man who does not desire

00:05:21.342 --> 00:05:24.122
to have money enough to buy all he wants is abnormal.

00:05:24.562 --> 00:05:26.682
There are three motives for which we live.

00:05:26.682 --> 00:05:30.422
We live for the body, we live for the mind, we live for the soul.

00:05:31.162 --> 00:05:33.982
No one of these is better or holier than the other.

00:05:34.382 --> 00:05:39.982
All are alike desirable, and no one of the three, body, mind or soul, can live fully

00:05:39.982 --> 00:05:43.402
if either of the others is cut short of full life and expression.

00:05:44.042 --> 00:05:49.082
It is not right or noble to live only for the soul and deny mind or body, and it is

00:05:49.082 --> 00:05:52.162
wrong to live for the intellect and deny body or soul.

00:05:52.162 --> 00:05:58.062
We are all acquainted with the lawsome consequences of living for the body and denying both mind

00:05:58.062 --> 00:06:03.002
and soul, and we can see that real life means the complete expression of all that man can

00:06:03.002 --> 00:06:05.402
give forth through body, mind and soul.

00:06:05.962 --> 00:06:10.882
Whatever he can say, no man can be really happy or satisfied unless his body is living

00:06:10.882 --> 00:06:15.282
fully in every function and unless the same is true for his mind and his soul.

00:06:16.042 --> 00:06:21.062
Wherever there is unexpressed possibility or function not performed, there is unsatisfied

00:06:21.062 --> 00:06:21.562
desire.

00:06:22.202 --> 00:06:26.722
Desire is possibility seeking expression or function seeking performance.

00:06:27.882 --> 00:06:32.802
Man cannot live fully in body without good food, comfortable clothing and warm shelter,

00:06:33.062 --> 00:06:35.302
and without freedom from excessive toil.

00:06:36.062 --> 00:06:39.682
Rest and recreation are also necessary for his physical life.

00:06:40.802 --> 00:06:45.442
He cannot live fully in mind without books and time to study them, without opportunity

00:06:45.442 --> 00:06:49.382
to travel and observation, or without intellectual companionship.

00:06:50.022 --> 00:06:55.182
To live fully in mind he must have intellectual recreations, and must surround himself with

00:06:55.182 --> 00:06:59.342
all the objects of art and beauty he is capable of using and appreciating.

00:07:00.082 --> 00:07:05.062
To live fully in soul, man must have love, and love is denied expression by poverty.

00:07:06.282 --> 00:07:10.382
A man's highest happiness is found in the bestowal of benefits on those he loves.

00:07:11.142 --> 00:07:14.622
Love finds its most natural and spontaneous expression in giving.

00:07:15.302 --> 00:07:20.282
The man who has nothing to give cannot fill his place as a husband or father, as a citizen

00:07:20.282 --> 00:07:21.162
or as a man.

00:07:22.022 --> 00:07:26.862
It is in the use of material things that the man finds full life for his body, develops

00:07:26.862 --> 00:07:28.962
his mind and unfolds his soul.

00:07:29.602 --> 00:07:33.122
It is therefore for supreme importance to him that he should be rich.

00:07:34.062 --> 00:07:36.842
It is perfectly right that you should desire to be rich.

00:07:37.142 --> 00:07:40.382
If you are a normal man or woman you cannot help doing so.

00:07:40.382 --> 00:07:44.262
It is perfectly right that you should give your best attention to the science of getting

00:07:44.262 --> 00:07:47.682
rich, for it is the noblest and most necessary of all studies.

00:07:48.382 --> 00:07:53.782
If you neglect this study you are derelict in your duty to yourself, to God and humanity,

00:07:54.502 --> 00:07:59.402
for you can render to God and humanity no greater service than to make the most of yourself.

00:08:18.571 --> 00:08:20.311
THERE IS A SCIENCE OF GETTING RICH.

00:08:21.691 --> 00:08:26.551
There is a science of getting rich, and it is an exact science, like algebra or arithmetic.

00:08:27.251 --> 00:08:30.371
There are certain laws which govern the process of acquiring riches.

00:08:30.951 --> 00:08:35.371
Once these laws are learned and obeyed by any man, he will get rich with mathematical

00:08:35.371 --> 00:08:35.991
certainty.

00:08:36.771 --> 00:08:41.551
The ownership of money and property comes as a result of doing things in a certain way.

00:08:42.111 --> 00:08:47.431
Those who do things in this certain way, whether on purpose or accidentally, get rich, while

00:08:47.431 --> 00:08:52.591
those who do not do things in this certain way, no matter how hard they work or how able

00:08:52.591 --> 00:08:54.191
they are, remain poor.

00:08:55.071 --> 00:09:00.371
It is a natural law that like causes always produce like effects, and therefore any man

00:09:00.371 --> 00:09:04.971
or woman who learns to do things in this certain way will infallibly get rich.

00:09:05.651 --> 00:09:08.991
That the above statement is true is shown by the following facts.

00:09:09.891 --> 00:09:14.331
Getting rich is not a matter of environment, for if it were, all the people in certain

00:09:14.331 --> 00:09:18.931
neighborhoods would become wealthy, the people of one city would be all rich, while those

00:09:18.931 --> 00:09:23.531
of other towns would all be poor, for the inhabitants of one state would roll in wealth,

00:09:24.111 --> 00:09:26.751
while those of an adjoining state would be in poverty.

00:09:26.871 --> 00:09:31.791
But everywhere we see rich and poor living side by side, in the same environment, and

00:09:31.791 --> 00:09:33.791
often engaged in the same vocations.

00:09:34.231 --> 00:09:39.071
When two men are in the same locality and in the same business, and one gets rich while

00:09:39.071 --> 00:09:43.871
the other remains poor, it shows that getting rich is not primarily a matter of environment.

00:09:44.451 --> 00:09:49.351
Some environments may be more favorable than others, but when two men in the same business

00:09:49.351 --> 00:09:54.191
are in the same neighborhood, and one gets rich while the other fails, it indicates that

00:09:54.191 --> 00:09:57.171
getting rich is a result of doing things in a certain way.

00:09:57.831 --> 00:10:02.951
And further, the ability to do things in this certain way is not due solely to the possession

00:10:02.951 --> 00:10:07.251
of talent, for many people who have great talent remain poor, while others who have

00:10:07.251 --> 00:10:08.951
very little talent get rich.

00:10:09.691 --> 00:10:14.651
Studying the people who have got rich, we find that they are an average lot in all respects,

00:10:15.111 --> 00:10:17.831
having no greater talents or abilities than other men.

00:10:18.151 --> 00:10:22.531
It is evident that they do not get rich because they possess talents or abilities that other

00:10:22.531 --> 00:10:26.291
men have not, but because they happen to do things in a certain way.

00:10:27.051 --> 00:10:32.051
Getting rich is not the result of saving or thrift, many very penurious people are poor,

00:10:32.051 --> 00:10:34.631
while free spenders often get rich.

00:10:35.071 --> 00:10:39.791
Nor is getting rich due to doing things which others fail to do, for two men in the same

00:10:39.791 --> 00:10:44.291
business often do almost exactly the same things, and one gets rich while the other

00:10:44.291 --> 00:10:46.291
remains poor or becomes bankrupt.

00:10:47.271 --> 00:10:51.271
From all these things, we must come to the conclusion that getting rich is the result

00:10:51.271 --> 00:10:53.051
of doing things in a certain way.

00:10:53.771 --> 00:10:58.731
If getting rich is the result of doing things in a certain way, and if like causes always

00:10:58.731 --> 00:11:03.851
produce like effects, then any man or woman who can do things in that way can become rich,

00:11:04.171 --> 00:11:07.531
and the whole matter is brought within the domain of exact science.

00:11:08.311 --> 00:11:13.091
The question arises here whether this certain way may not be so difficult that only a few

00:11:13.091 --> 00:11:14.031
may follow it.

00:11:14.271 --> 00:11:18.691
This cannot be true, as we have seen, so far as natural ability is concerned.

00:11:19.251 --> 00:11:22.291
Talented people get rich, and blockheads get rich.

00:11:23.091 --> 00:11:26.651
Intellectually brilliant people get rich, and very stupid people get rich.

00:11:26.651 --> 00:11:31.071
Physically strong people get rich, and weak and sickly people get rich.

00:11:31.631 --> 00:11:35.311
Some degree of ability to think and understand is, of course, essential.

00:11:35.851 --> 00:11:40.631
But in so far natural ability is concerned, any man or woman who has sense enough to read

00:11:40.631 --> 00:11:43.171
and understand these words can certainly get rich.

00:11:43.931 --> 00:11:46.551
Also, we have seen that it is not a matter of environment.

00:11:47.131 --> 00:11:51.731
Location counts for something, one would not go to the heart of the Sahara and expect to

00:11:51.731 --> 00:11:52.911
do successful business.

00:11:53.451 --> 00:11:58.211
Getting rich involves the necessity of dealing with man, and of being where there are people

00:11:58.211 --> 00:11:58.971
to deal with.

00:11:59.311 --> 00:12:03.811
And if these people are inclined to deal in the way you want to deal, so much the better.

00:12:04.171 --> 00:12:06.471
But that is about as far as environment goes.

00:12:06.991 --> 00:12:10.011
If anybody else in your town can get rich, so can you.

00:12:10.331 --> 00:12:13.631
And if anybody else in your state can get rich, so can you.

00:12:14.311 --> 00:12:17.911
Again, it is not a matter of choosing some particular business or profession.

00:12:18.491 --> 00:12:21.331
People get rich in every business and in every profession.

00:12:21.891 --> 00:12:25.531
While their next-door neighbours on the same vacation remain in poverty.

00:12:26.351 --> 00:12:30.851
It is true that you will do best in a business which you like and which is congenial to you.

00:12:31.231 --> 00:12:35.271
And if you have certain talents which are well developed, you will do best in a business

00:12:35.271 --> 00:12:37.431
which calls for the exercise of those talents.

00:12:38.771 --> 00:12:42.331
Also, you will do best in a business which is suited to your locality.

00:12:42.671 --> 00:12:47.051
An ice-cream parlour would do better in a warm climate than in Greenland, and a salmon

00:12:47.051 --> 00:12:51.411
fishery would succeed better in the north-west than in Florida, where there are no salmon.

00:12:52.111 --> 00:12:56.831
But aside from these general limitations, getting rich is not dependent upon your engaging

00:12:56.831 --> 00:13:01.231
in some particular business, but upon your learning to do things in a certain way.

00:13:01.491 --> 00:13:05.411
If you are now in business and everybody else in your locality is getting rich in the same

00:13:05.411 --> 00:13:09.211
business while you are not getting rich, it is because you are not doing things in the

00:13:09.211 --> 00:13:11.331
same way that the other person is doing them.

00:13:12.011 --> 00:13:14.751
No one is prevented from getting rich by lack of capital.

00:13:15.331 --> 00:13:20.111
True, as you get capital the increase becomes more easy and rapid, but one who has capital

00:13:20.111 --> 00:13:23.731
is already rich, and does not need to consider how to become so.

00:13:24.191 --> 00:13:29.011
No matter how poor you may be, if you begin to do things in a certain way, you will begin

00:13:29.011 --> 00:13:31.711
to get rich, and you will begin to have capital.

00:13:32.371 --> 00:13:37.231
The getting of capital is a part of the process of getting rich, and it is a part of the result

00:13:37.231 --> 00:13:40.711
which invariably follows the doing of things in a certain way.

00:13:40.711 --> 00:13:44.511
You may be the poorest man on the continent, and be deeply in debt.

00:13:44.811 --> 00:13:49.631
You may have neither friends, influence, nor resources, but if you begin to do things in

00:13:49.631 --> 00:13:55.371
this way, you must infallibly begin to get rich, for like causes must produce like effects.

00:13:55.851 --> 00:13:58.131
If you have no capital, you can get capital.

00:13:58.611 --> 00:14:01.711
If you are in the wrong business, you can get into the right business.

00:14:02.151 --> 00:14:06.611
If you are in the wrong location, you can go to the right location, and you can do so

00:14:06.611 --> 00:14:11.771
in your present business and in your present location, to do things in a certain way which

00:14:11.771 --> 00:14:12.891
causes success.

00:14:32.472 --> 00:14:34.652
IS OPPORTUNITY MONOPOLISED?

00:14:35.592 --> 00:14:40.252
No man is kept poor because opportunity has been taken away from him, because other people

00:14:40.252 --> 00:14:43.432
have monopolised the wealth and have put a fence around it.

00:14:43.652 --> 00:14:48.132
You may be shut off from engaging in business in certain lines, but there are other channels

00:14:48.132 --> 00:14:49.032
open to you.

00:14:49.032 --> 00:14:53.472
Probably it would be hard for you to get control of any of the great rail-load systems.

00:14:53.872 --> 00:14:55.732
That field is pretty well monopolised.

00:14:56.232 --> 00:15:00.832
But the electric railway business is still in its infancy, and offers plenty of scope

00:15:00.832 --> 00:15:01.732
for enterprise.

00:15:02.332 --> 00:15:06.832
And it will be with a few years, until traffic and transportation through the air will become

00:15:06.832 --> 00:15:11.412
a great industry, and in all its branches will give employment to hundreds of thousands

00:15:11.412 --> 00:15:13.172
and perhaps to millions of people.

00:15:13.632 --> 00:15:18.672
Why not turn your attention to the development of aerial transportation, instead of competing

00:15:18.672 --> 00:15:22.432
with J.J. Hill and others for a chance in the steam railway world?

00:15:23.232 --> 00:15:27.532
It is quite true that if you are a workman in the employ of the steel-trust, you have

00:15:27.532 --> 00:15:30.712
very little chance of becoming the owner of the plant in which you work.

00:15:31.012 --> 00:15:35.772
But it is also true that if you will commence the act in a certain way, you can soon leave

00:15:35.772 --> 00:15:37.272
the employ of the steel-trust.

00:15:37.532 --> 00:15:43.392
You can buy a farm of from 10 to 40 acres, and engage in business as a producer of foodstuffs.

00:15:43.852 --> 00:15:48.572
There is great opportunity at this time for men, who will live upon small tracts of land

00:15:48.572 --> 00:15:50.692
and cultivate the same intensively.

00:15:51.072 --> 00:15:52.832
Such men will certainly get rich.

00:15:53.292 --> 00:15:57.352
You may say that it is impossible for you to get the land, but I am going to prove to

00:15:57.352 --> 00:16:01.812
you that it is not impossible, and that you can certainly get a farm if you will go to

00:16:01.812 --> 00:16:02.972
work in a certain way.

00:16:03.512 --> 00:16:08.552
At different periods, the tide of opportunity sets in different directions, according to

00:16:08.552 --> 00:16:13.252
needs of the whole, and the particular state of social evolution which has been reached.

00:16:13.732 --> 00:16:18.972
At present, in America, it is setting toward agriculture and the allied industries and

00:16:18.972 --> 00:16:19.592
professions.

00:16:20.212 --> 00:16:23.832
Today, opportunity is open before the factory worker in his line.

00:16:24.172 --> 00:16:28.832
It is open before the businessman, who supplies the farmer more than before the one who supplies

00:16:28.832 --> 00:16:33.852
the factory worker, and before the professional man, who waits upon the farmer more than before

00:16:33.852 --> 00:16:35.672
the one who serves the working class.

00:16:35.672 --> 00:16:40.412
There is abundance of opportunity for the man who will go with the tide, instead of

00:16:40.412 --> 00:16:41.892
trying to swim against it.

00:16:42.372 --> 00:16:47.832
So the factory workers, either as individuals or as a class, are not deprived of opportunity.

00:16:48.292 --> 00:16:50.932
The workers are not being kept down by their masters.

00:16:51.412 --> 00:16:54.752
They are not being ground by the trusts and combinations of capital.

00:16:55.272 --> 00:16:59.512
As a class, they are where they are because they do not do things in a certain way.

00:16:59.992 --> 00:17:04.772
If the workers of America chose to do so, they could follow the example of their brothers

00:17:04.772 --> 00:17:10.052
in Belgium and other countries, and establish great department stores and cooperative industries.

00:17:10.672 --> 00:17:15.432
They could elect men of their own class to office, and pass laws favoring the development

00:17:15.432 --> 00:17:20.572
of such cooperative industries, and in a few years they could take peaceable possession

00:17:20.572 --> 00:17:22.052
of the industrial field.

00:17:23.132 --> 00:17:27.572
The working class may become the master class whenever they will begin to do things in a

00:17:27.572 --> 00:17:28.192
certain way.

00:17:28.372 --> 00:17:31.772
The law of wealth is the same for them as it is for all others.

00:17:32.252 --> 00:17:37.212
This they must learn, and they will remain where they are, as long as they continue to

00:17:37.212 --> 00:17:38.072
do as they do.

00:17:38.432 --> 00:17:44.092
The individual worker, however, is not held down by the ignorance or the mental slothfulness

00:17:44.092 --> 00:17:44.952
of his class.

00:17:45.452 --> 00:17:50.032
He can follow the tide of opportunity to riches, and this book will tell them how.

00:17:50.792 --> 00:17:54.232
No one is kept in poverty by a shortness in the supply of riches.

00:17:54.612 --> 00:17:56.132
There is more than enough for all.

00:17:56.432 --> 00:18:01.132
A palace as large as the capital at Washington might be built for every family on earth,

00:18:01.132 --> 00:18:06.472
from the building material in the United States alone, and under intensive cultivation this

00:18:06.472 --> 00:18:11.532
country would produce wool, cotton, linen, and silk enough to cloth each person in the

00:18:11.532 --> 00:18:16.092
world finer than Solomon was arrayed in all his glory, together with food enough to feed

00:18:16.092 --> 00:18:17.472
them all luxuriously.

00:18:18.032 --> 00:18:23.972
The visible supply is practically inexhaustible, and the invisible supply really is inexhaustible.

00:18:24.592 --> 00:18:29.152
Everything you see on earth is made from one original substance, out of which all things

00:18:29.152 --> 00:18:29.672
proceed.

00:18:30.652 --> 00:18:36.852
New forms are constantly being made, and older ones are dissolving, but all are shapes assumed

00:18:36.852 --> 00:18:37.832
by one thing.

00:18:38.792 --> 00:18:43.072
There is no limit to the supply of formless stuff or original substance.

00:18:43.772 --> 00:18:47.932
The universe is made out of it, but it is not all used in making the universe.

00:18:48.452 --> 00:18:53.352
The spaces in, through, and between the forms of the visible universe are permeated and

00:18:53.352 --> 00:18:57.852
filled with the original substance, with the formless stuff, with the raw material of all

00:18:57.852 --> 00:18:58.272
things.

00:18:58.832 --> 00:19:03.752
Ten thousand times as much as has been made might still be made, and even then we should

00:19:03.752 --> 00:19:06.772
not have exhausted the supply of universal raw material.

00:19:07.472 --> 00:19:11.952
No man, therefore, is poor because nature is poor, or because there is not enough to

00:19:11.952 --> 00:19:12.572
go around.

00:19:13.292 --> 00:19:15.912
Nature is an inexhaustible storehouse of riches.

00:19:16.372 --> 00:19:18.272
The supply will never run short.

00:19:18.872 --> 00:19:24.052
Original substance is alive with creative energy, and is constantly producing more forms.

00:19:24.652 --> 00:19:28.512
When the supply of building material is exhausted, more will be produced.

00:19:28.852 --> 00:19:33.652
When the soil is exhausted, so that foodstuffs and materials for clothing will no longer

00:19:33.652 --> 00:19:37.412
grow upon it, it will be renewed, or more soil will be made.

00:19:37.972 --> 00:19:42.372
When all the gold and silver has been dug from the earth, if man is still in such a

00:19:42.372 --> 00:19:46.712
stage of social development that he needs gold and silver, more will be produced from

00:19:46.712 --> 00:19:47.432
the formless.

00:19:47.852 --> 00:19:50.492
The formless stuff responds to the needs of man.

00:19:50.492 --> 00:19:53.132
It will not let him be without any good thing.

00:19:54.172 --> 00:19:55.912
This is true of man collectively.

00:19:56.472 --> 00:20:01.512
The race as a whole is always abundantly rich, and if individuals are poor, it is because

00:20:01.512 --> 00:20:06.312
they do not follow the certain way of doing things, which makes the individual man rich.

00:20:06.992 --> 00:20:08.692
The formless stuff is intelligent.

00:20:09.172 --> 00:20:10.712
It is stuff which thinks.

00:20:11.212 --> 00:20:14.332
It is alive, and is always impelled toward more life.

00:20:14.932 --> 00:20:18.672
It is the natural and inherent impulse of life to seek to live more.

00:20:18.672 --> 00:20:23.832
It is the nature of intelligence to enlarge itself, and of consciousness to seek to extend

00:20:23.832 --> 00:20:26.232
its boundaries and find fuller expression.

00:20:27.292 --> 00:20:32.492
The universe of forms has been made by formless living substance, throwing itself into form

00:20:32.492 --> 00:20:34.752
in order to express itself more fully.

00:20:35.532 --> 00:20:40.772
The universe is a great living presence, always moving inherently toward more life and fuller

00:20:40.772 --> 00:20:41.232
functioning.

00:20:42.052 --> 00:20:44.572
Nature is formed for the advancement of life.

00:20:45.072 --> 00:20:47.532
Its impelling motive is the increase of life.

00:20:47.952 --> 00:20:52.712
For this cause, everything which can possibly minister to life is bountifully provided.

00:20:53.132 --> 00:20:57.672
There can be no lack unless God is to contradict Himself and nullify His own works.

00:20:58.212 --> 00:21:01.272
You are not kept poor by lacking the supply of riches.

00:21:01.732 --> 00:21:06.692
It is a fact that I shall demonstrate a little farther on, that even the resources of the

00:21:06.692 --> 00:21:11.292
formless supply are at the command of the man or woman, who will act and think in a

00:21:11.292 --> 00:21:12.052
certain way.

00:21:31.620 --> 00:21:34.460
THE FIRST PRINCIPLE IN THE SCIENCE OF GETTING RICH

00:21:35.340 --> 00:21:39.920
Thought is the only power which can produce tangible riches from the formless substance.

00:21:40.620 --> 00:21:45.460
The stuff, from which all things are made, is a substance which thinks, and the thought

00:21:45.460 --> 00:21:47.920
of form in this substance produces the form.

00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:51.720
Original substance moves according to its thoughts.

00:21:52.360 --> 00:21:56.960
Every form and process you see in nature is the visible expression of a thought in original

00:21:56.960 --> 00:21:57.560
substance.

00:21:58.320 --> 00:22:01.740
As the formless stuff thinks of a form, it takes that form.

00:22:02.060 --> 00:22:04.840
As it thinks of a motion, it makes that motion.

00:22:05.720 --> 00:22:08.060
That is the way all things were created.

00:22:08.580 --> 00:22:11.900
We live in a thought-world which is part of a thought-universe.

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:16.980
The thought of a moving universe extended throughout formless substance, and the thinking

00:22:16.980 --> 00:22:22.040
stuff moving according to that thought took the form of systems of planets and maintains

00:22:22.040 --> 00:22:22.680
that form.

00:22:23.300 --> 00:22:27.720
Thinking substance takes the form of its thought and moves according to the thought.

00:22:28.260 --> 00:22:33.560
Holding the idea of a circling system of sounds and worlds, it takes the form of these bodies

00:22:33.560 --> 00:22:35.660
and moves them as it thinks.

00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:41.720
Thinking the form of a slow-growing oak tree, it moves accordingly and produces the tree,

00:22:42.100 --> 00:22:44.720
though centuries may be required to do the work.

00:22:45.300 --> 00:22:50.200
In creating, the formless seems to move according to the lines of motion it has established.

00:22:50.620 --> 00:22:54.860
The thought of an oak tree does not cause the instant formation of a full-grown tree,

00:22:55.240 --> 00:23:00.120
but it does start in motion the forces which will produce the tree along established lines

00:23:00.120 --> 00:23:00.800
of growth.

00:23:01.980 --> 00:23:07.660
Every thought of form, held in thinking substance, causes the creation of the form, but always,

00:23:07.780 --> 00:23:12.300
or at least generally, along lines of growth and action already established.

00:23:13.180 --> 00:23:18.560
The thought of a house of a certain construction, if it were impressed upon formless substance,

00:23:18.940 --> 00:23:23.760
might not cause the instant formation of the house, but it would cause the turning of creative

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:28.840
energies already working in trade and commerce into such channels as to result in the speedy

00:23:28.840 --> 00:23:30.000
building of the house.

00:23:30.460 --> 00:23:35.160
And if there were no existing channels through which the creative energy could work, then

00:23:35.160 --> 00:23:40.560
the house would be formed directly from primal substance, without waiting for the slow processes

00:23:40.560 --> 00:23:42.680
of the organic and inorganic world.

00:23:43.540 --> 00:23:48.560
No thought of form can be impressed upon original substance without causing the creation of

00:23:48.560 --> 00:23:49.040
the form.

00:23:50.040 --> 00:23:53.180
Man is a thinking center and can originate thought.

00:23:54.220 --> 00:23:58.860
All the forms that man fashions with his hands must first exist in his thought.

00:23:59.460 --> 00:24:02.760
He cannot shape a thing until he has thought that thing.

00:24:03.200 --> 00:24:07.220
And so far man has confined his efforts wholly to the work of his hands.

00:24:07.220 --> 00:24:12.940
He has applied manual labor to the world of forms, seeking the change or modify those

00:24:12.940 --> 00:24:14.040
already existing.

00:24:14.660 --> 00:24:19.900
He has never thought of trying to cause the creation of new forms by impressing his thoughts

00:24:19.900 --> 00:24:21.360
upon formless substance.

00:24:22.160 --> 00:24:27.480
When man has a thought-form, he takes material from the forms of nature, and makes an image

00:24:27.480 --> 00:24:29.240
of the form which is in his mind.

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:35.380
He has so far made little or no effort to cooperate with formless intelligence, to work

00:24:35.380 --> 00:24:36.160
with the Father.

00:24:36.160 --> 00:24:40.040
He has not dreamed that he can do what he sees the Father doing.

00:24:40.600 --> 00:24:44.500
Man reshapes and modifies existing forms by manual labor.

00:24:44.920 --> 00:24:49.440
He has given no attention to the question whether he may not produce things from formless

00:24:49.440 --> 00:24:52.020
substance by communicating his thoughts to it.

00:24:52.480 --> 00:24:57.940
We propose to prove that he may do so, to prove that any man or woman may do so, and

00:24:57.940 --> 00:24:58.900
to show how.

00:24:59.320 --> 00:25:03.720
As our first step, we must lay down three fundamental propositions.

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:10.000
First, we assert that there is one original formless stuff or substance from which all

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:10.900
things are made.

00:25:11.540 --> 00:25:15.780
All the seemingly many elements are but different presentations of one element.

00:25:16.460 --> 00:25:21.840
All the many forms found in organic and inorganic nature are but different shapes, made from

00:25:21.840 --> 00:25:22.720
the same stuff.

00:25:23.560 --> 00:25:25.440
And this stuff is thinking stuff.

00:25:26.080 --> 00:25:28.900
A thought held in it produces the form of the thought.

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:32.440
Thought in thinking substance produces shapes.

00:25:33.020 --> 00:25:36.500
Man is a thinking center, capable of original thought.

00:25:37.380 --> 00:25:42.900
If man can communicate his thoughts to original thinking substance, he can cause the creation

00:25:42.900 --> 00:25:45.580
or formation of the thing he thinks about.

00:25:46.020 --> 00:25:51.120
To summarize this, there is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which,

00:25:51.240 --> 00:25:56.700
in its original state, permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

00:25:57.360 --> 00:26:02.420
A thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

00:26:03.080 --> 00:26:08.440
Man can form things in his thought, and by impressing his thought upon formless substance,

00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:11.380
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

00:26:12.180 --> 00:26:17.760
It may be asked if I can prove these statements, and without going into details, I answer that

00:26:17.760 --> 00:26:21.000
I can do so, both by logic and experience.

00:26:21.880 --> 00:26:26.700
Reasoning back from the phenomena of form and thought, I come to one original thinking

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:31.800
substance, and reasoning forward from this thinking substance, I come to man's power

00:26:31.800 --> 00:26:34.460
to cause the formation of the thing he thinks about.

00:26:35.020 --> 00:26:40.260
And by experiment, I find the reasoning true, and this is my strongest proof.

00:26:40.920 --> 00:26:46.000
If one man who reads this book gets rich by doing what he tells him to do, that is evidence

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:47.340
in support of my claim.

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:53.180
But if every man who does what he tells him to do gets rich, that is positive proof until

00:26:53.180 --> 00:26:55.540
someone goes through the process and fails.

00:26:56.120 --> 00:27:01.720
The theory is true until the process fails, and this process will not fail, for every

00:27:01.720 --> 00:27:05.400
man who does exactly what this book tells him to do will get rich.

00:27:06.180 --> 00:27:12.020
I have said that man gets rich by doing things in a certain way, and in order to do so, man

00:27:12.020 --> 00:27:14.420
must become able to think in a certain way.

00:27:14.900 --> 00:27:19.860
A man's way of doing things is the direct result of the way he thinks about things.

00:27:20.700 --> 00:27:25.380
To do things in a way you want to do them, you will have to acquire the ability to think

00:27:25.380 --> 00:27:26.700
the way you want to think.

00:27:27.240 --> 00:27:29.640
This is the first step toward getting rich.

00:27:30.420 --> 00:27:34.820
To think what you want to think is to think truth, regardless of appearances.

00:27:35.960 --> 00:27:40.900
Every man has the natural and inherent power to think what he wants to think, but it requires

00:27:40.900 --> 00:27:45.060
far more effort to do so than it does to think the thoughts which are suggested by

00:27:45.060 --> 00:27:45.680
appearances.

00:27:46.360 --> 00:27:48.620
To think according to appearance is easy.

00:27:48.980 --> 00:27:53.940
To think truth, regardless of appearances, is laborious, and requires the expenditure

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:57.540
of more power than any other work man is called upon to perform.

00:27:58.180 --> 00:28:03.340
There is no labor from which most people shrink as they do from that of sustained and consecutive

00:28:03.340 --> 00:28:03.840
thought.

00:28:04.300 --> 00:28:06.100
It is the hardest work in the world.

00:28:06.580 --> 00:28:10.460
This is especially true when truth is contrary to appearances.

00:28:11.300 --> 00:28:16.340
Every appearance in the visible world tends to produce a corresponding form in the mind

00:28:16.340 --> 00:28:21.040
which observes it, and this can only be prevented by holding the thought of the truth.

00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:26.600
To look upon the appearance of disease will produce the form of disease in your own mind,

00:28:26.860 --> 00:28:28.360
and ultimately in your body.

00:28:28.740 --> 00:28:33.060
Unless you hold the thought of the truth, which is that there is no disease, it is only

00:28:33.580 --> 00:28:35.600
and the reality is health.

00:28:36.300 --> 00:28:41.040
To look upon the appearances of poverty will produce corresponding forms in your own mind,

00:28:41.360 --> 00:28:45.880
unless you hold to the truth that there is no poverty, there is only abundance.

00:28:46.600 --> 00:28:51.860
To think health when surrounded by the appearances of disease, or to think riches when in the

00:28:51.860 --> 00:28:54.700
midst of appearances of poverty, requires power.

00:28:55.240 --> 00:28:58.440
But he who acquires this power becomes a mastermind.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.220
He can conquer fate.

00:29:00.560 --> 00:29:01.960
He can have what he wants.

00:29:02.760 --> 00:29:07.800
This power can only be acquired by getting hold of the basic fact which is behind all

00:29:07.800 --> 00:29:13.400
appearances, and that fact is that there is one thinking substance from which and by which

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.480
all things are made.

00:29:15.020 --> 00:29:20.680
Then we must grasp the truth that every thought held in the substance becomes a form, and

00:29:20.680 --> 00:29:25.480
that man can so impress his thoughts upon it as to cause them to take form and become

00:29:25.480 --> 00:29:26.480
visible things.

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:32.780
When we realize this, we lose all doubt and fear, for we know that we can create we want

00:29:32.780 --> 00:29:37.280
to create, we can get what we want to have, and can become what we want to be.

00:29:37.780 --> 00:29:42.700
As a first step toward getting rich, you must believe the three fundamental statements given

00:29:42.700 --> 00:29:47.200
previously in this chapter, and in order to emphasize them, I repeat them here.

00:29:48.120 --> 00:29:52.900
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

00:29:52.900 --> 00:29:56.860
permits, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

00:29:57.840 --> 00:30:02.320
The thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

00:30:03.180 --> 00:30:08.520
Man can form things in his thought, and, by impressing his thought upon formless substance,

00:30:08.900 --> 00:30:11.980
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

00:30:12.940 --> 00:30:17.900
You must lay aside all other concepts of the universe than this monistic one, and you must

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:22.600
dwell upon this until it is fixed in your mind, and has become your habitual thought.

00:30:23.280 --> 00:30:29.180
Read discrete statements over and over again, fix every word upon your memory, and meditate

00:30:29.180 --> 00:30:31.700
upon them until you firmly believe what they say.

00:30:32.260 --> 00:30:35.140
If a doubt comes to you, cast it aside as a sin.

00:30:35.800 --> 00:30:38.180
Do not listen to arguments against this idea.

00:30:38.580 --> 00:30:43.580
Do not go to churches or lectures where a contrary concept of things is thought or preached.

00:30:44.060 --> 00:30:47.500
Do not read magazines or books which teach a different idea.

00:30:48.000 --> 00:30:51.720
If you get mixed up in your faith, all your efforts will be in vain.

00:30:52.680 --> 00:30:57.520
Do not ask why these things are true, nor speculate as to how they can be true.

00:30:57.820 --> 00:30:59.240
Simply take them on trust.

00:30:59.740 --> 00:31:03.700
The science of getting rich begins with the absolute acceptance of this faith.

00:31:23.971 --> 00:31:29.131
You must get rid of the last vestige of the old idea that there is a deity whose will

00:31:29.131 --> 00:31:34.091
it is that you should be poor, or whose purposes may be served by keeping you in poverty.

00:31:34.751 --> 00:31:39.211
The intelligent substance which is all, and in all, and which lives in all, and lives

00:31:39.211 --> 00:31:41.851
in you, is a consciously living substance.

00:31:42.391 --> 00:31:47.131
Being a consciously living substance, it must have the nature and inherent desire of every

00:31:47.131 --> 00:31:49.371
living intelligence for increase of life.

00:31:49.991 --> 00:31:54.871
Every living thing must continually seek for the enlargement of its life, because life,

00:31:54.971 --> 00:31:57.571
in the mere act of living, must increase itself.

00:31:58.291 --> 00:32:04.251
A seed, dropped into the ground, springs into activity, and in the act of living produces

00:32:04.251 --> 00:32:05.411
a hundred more seeds.

00:32:05.871 --> 00:32:08.211
Life by living multiplies itself.

00:32:08.211 --> 00:32:10.311
It is forever becoming more.

00:32:10.491 --> 00:32:13.171
It must do so if it continues to be at all.

00:32:14.071 --> 00:32:17.291
Intelligence is under the same necessity for continuous increase.

00:32:17.791 --> 00:32:22.051
Every thought we think makes it necessary for us to think another thought.

00:32:22.931 --> 00:32:24.671
Consciousness is continually expanding.

00:32:25.511 --> 00:32:28.771
Every fact we learn leads us to the learning of another fact.

00:32:29.131 --> 00:32:31.091
Knowledge is continually increasing.

00:32:32.171 --> 00:32:36.691
Every talent we cultivate brings to the mind a desire to cultivate another talent.

00:32:36.691 --> 00:32:42.251
We are subject to the urge of life, seeking expression, whichever drives us on to know

00:32:42.251 --> 00:32:44.551
more, to do more, and to be more.

00:32:45.211 --> 00:32:49.171
In order to know more, do more, and be more, we must have more.

00:32:49.611 --> 00:32:55.211
We must have things to use, for we learn, and do, and become, only by using things.

00:32:55.691 --> 00:32:58.411
We must get rich, so that we can live more.

00:32:59.431 --> 00:33:04.071
The desire for riches is simply the capacity for larger life seeking fulfilment.

00:33:04.611 --> 00:33:08.811
Every desire is the effort of an unexpressed possibility to come into action.

00:33:09.331 --> 00:33:12.531
It is power seeking to manifest which causes desire.

00:33:13.431 --> 00:33:17.951
That which makes you want more money is the same as that which makes the plant grow.

00:33:18.451 --> 00:33:20.911
It is life, seeking fuller expression.

00:33:21.891 --> 00:33:25.631
The one living substance must be subject to this inherent law of all life.

00:33:26.011 --> 00:33:28.351
It is permitted with the desire to live more.

00:33:28.671 --> 00:33:31.551
That is why it is under the necessity of creating things.

00:33:32.051 --> 00:33:37.051
The one substance desires to live more in you, hence it wants you to have all the things

00:33:37.051 --> 00:33:37.851
you can use.

00:33:38.711 --> 00:33:41.071
It is the desire of God that you should get rich.

00:33:41.571 --> 00:33:46.211
He wants you to get rich, because he can express himself better through you if you have plenty

00:33:46.211 --> 00:33:48.371
of things to use in giving him expression.

00:33:49.071 --> 00:33:53.231
He can live more in you if you have unlimited command of the means of life.

00:33:54.071 --> 00:33:56.951
The universe desires you to have everything you want to have.

00:33:57.371 --> 00:33:59.091
Nature is friendly to your plans.

00:33:59.751 --> 00:34:01.791
Everything is naturally for you.

00:34:02.391 --> 00:34:04.391
Make up your mind that this is true.

00:34:05.251 --> 00:34:09.511
It is essential, however, that your purpose should harmonise with the purpose that is

00:34:09.511 --> 00:34:09.951
in all.

00:34:10.771 --> 00:34:14.451
You must want real life, not mere pleasure of sensual gratification.

00:34:15.211 --> 00:34:20.251
Life is the performance of function, and the individual really lives only when he performs

00:34:20.251 --> 00:34:25.671
every function, physical, mental and spiritual, of which he is capable, without excess in

00:34:25.671 --> 00:34:25.911
any.

00:34:26.591 --> 00:34:31.351
You do not want to get rich in order to live swinishly, for the gratification of animal

00:34:31.351 --> 00:34:33.271
desires, that is not life.

00:34:33.751 --> 00:34:38.791
But the performance of every physical function is a part of life, and no one lives completely

00:34:38.791 --> 00:34:42.571
who denies the impulses of the body a normal and healthful expression.

00:34:43.851 --> 00:34:48.711
You do not want to get rich solely to enjoy mental pleasures, to get knowledge, to gratify

00:34:48.711 --> 00:34:51.451
ambition, to outshine others, to be famous.

00:34:51.951 --> 00:34:56.411
All these are legitimate part of life, but the man who lives for the pleasures of the

00:34:56.411 --> 00:35:01.391
intellect alone will only have a partial life, and he will never be satisfied with his lot.

00:35:02.431 --> 00:35:07.211
You do not want to get rich solely for the good of others, to lose yourself for the salvation

00:35:07.211 --> 00:35:11.311
of mankind, to experience the joys of philanthropy and sacrifice.

00:35:12.071 --> 00:35:17.291
The joys of the soul are only a part of life, and they are no better nor nobler than any

00:35:17.291 --> 00:35:17.891
other part.

00:35:18.931 --> 00:35:24.111
You want to get rich in order that you may eat, drink, and be merry when it is time to

00:35:24.111 --> 00:35:29.311
do these things, in order that you may surround yourself with beautiful things, see distant

00:35:29.311 --> 00:35:35.031
lands, feed your mind, and develop your intellect, in order that you may love man and do kind

00:35:35.031 --> 00:35:39.251
things, and be able to play a good part in helping the world to find truth.

00:35:39.711 --> 00:35:45.071
But remember that extreme altruism is no better nor nobler than extreme selfishness.

00:35:45.211 --> 00:35:46.331
Both are mistakes.

00:35:47.091 --> 00:35:51.831
Get rid of the idea that God wants you to sacrifice yourself for others, and that you

00:35:51.831 --> 00:35:54.011
can secure His favor by doing so.

00:35:54.371 --> 00:35:56.291
God requires nothing of the kind.

00:35:57.031 --> 00:36:01.311
What He wants you is that you should make the most of yourself for yourself and for

00:36:01.311 --> 00:36:06.471
others, and you can help others more by making the most of yourself than in any other way.

00:36:06.971 --> 00:36:11.791
You can make the most of yourself only by getting rich, so it is right and praiseworthy

00:36:11.791 --> 00:36:15.811
that you should give your first and best thought to the work of acquiring wealth.

00:36:16.671 --> 00:36:22.151
Remember however that the desire of substance is for all, and its movements must be for

00:36:22.151 --> 00:36:23.191
more life to all.

00:36:23.551 --> 00:36:28.371
It cannot be made to work for less life to any, because it is equally in all, seeking

00:36:28.371 --> 00:36:29.431
riches and life.

00:36:30.451 --> 00:36:34.671
Intelligent substance will make things for you, but it will not take things away from

00:36:34.671 --> 00:36:36.491
someone else and give them to you.

00:36:37.191 --> 00:36:39.251
You must get rid of the thought of competition.

00:36:39.251 --> 00:36:43.231
You are to create, not to compete for what is already created.

00:36:44.071 --> 00:36:46.111
You do not have to take anything from anyone.

00:36:46.991 --> 00:36:49.291
You do not have to drive sharp bargains.

00:36:50.011 --> 00:36:52.571
You do not have to cheat, or to take advantage.

00:36:52.951 --> 00:36:56.311
You do not need to let any man work for you for less than he earns.

00:36:57.691 --> 00:37:02.031
You do not have to covet the property of others, or to look at it with twistful eyes.

00:37:02.431 --> 00:37:06.751
No man has anything of which you cannot have the like, and that without taking what he

00:37:06.751 --> 00:37:07.891
has away from him.

00:37:07.891 --> 00:37:11.251
You are to become a creator, not a competitor.

00:37:11.811 --> 00:37:16.411
You are going to get what you want, but in such a way that when you get it every other

00:37:16.411 --> 00:37:18.291
man will have more than he has now.

00:37:18.731 --> 00:37:23.611
I am aware that there are men who get a vast amount of money by proceeding in direct opposition

00:37:23.611 --> 00:37:28.011
to the statements in the paragraph above, and may add a word of explanation here.

00:37:28.611 --> 00:37:34.531
Men of the plutocratic type, who become very rich, do so sometimes purely by their extraordinary

00:37:34.531 --> 00:37:39.871
on the plane of competition, and sometimes they unconsciously relate themselves to substance

00:37:39.871 --> 00:37:44.731
in its great purposes and movements for the general racial upbuilding through industrial

00:37:44.731 --> 00:37:45.331
evolution.

00:37:45.991 --> 00:37:51.031
Rockefeller, Carnegie, Morgan, and others have been the unconscious agents of the supreme

00:37:51.031 --> 00:37:55.711
in the necessary work of systematizing and organizing productive industry, and in the

00:37:55.711 --> 00:37:59.631
end their work will contribute immensely toward increased life for all.

00:38:00.331 --> 00:38:01.851
Their day is nearly over.

00:38:01.851 --> 00:38:06.891
They have organized production, and will soon be succeeded by the agents of the multitude

00:38:06.891 --> 00:38:09.471
who will organize the machinery of distribution.

00:38:10.831 --> 00:38:14.851
The multimillionaires are like the monster reptiles of the prehistoric eras.

00:38:15.171 --> 00:38:20.071
They play a necessary part in the evolutionary process, but the same power which produced

00:38:20.071 --> 00:38:24.811
them will dispose of them, and it is well to bear in mind that they have never been

00:38:24.811 --> 00:38:25.551
really rich.

00:38:25.911 --> 00:38:30.591
A record of the private lives of most of this class will show that they have really been

00:38:30.591 --> 00:38:32.751
the most abject and wretched of the poor.

00:38:33.431 --> 00:38:37.431
Riches secured on the competitive plane are never satisfactory and permanent.

00:38:37.751 --> 00:38:40.051
They are yours today and another's tomorrow.

00:38:40.551 --> 00:38:46.371
Remember, if you are to become rich in a scientific and certain way, you must rise entirely out

00:38:46.371 --> 00:38:47.611
of the competitive thought.

00:38:48.151 --> 00:38:51.171
You must never think for a moment that the supply is limited.

00:38:51.671 --> 00:38:55.871
Just as soon as you begin to think that all the money is being cornered and controlled

00:38:56.331 --> 00:39:01.491
and others, and that you must exert yourself to get laws passed to stop this process and

00:39:01.491 --> 00:39:07.471
so on, in that moment you drop into the competitive mind, and your power to cause creation is

00:39:07.471 --> 00:39:08.651
gone for the time being.

00:39:08.951 --> 00:39:13.891
And what is worse, you will probably arrest the creative movements you have already instituted.

00:39:14.571 --> 00:39:18.491
Know that there are countless millions of dollars worth of gold in the mountains of

00:39:18.491 --> 00:39:23.731
the earth not yet brought to light, and know that if there were not, more would be created

00:39:23.731 --> 00:39:26.151
from thinking substance to supply your needs.

00:39:26.891 --> 00:39:31.511
Know that the money you need will come, even if it is necessary for a thousand men to be

00:39:31.511 --> 00:39:34.011
led to the discovery of new gold mines tomorrow.

00:39:34.851 --> 00:39:39.731
Never look at the visible supply, look always at the limitless riches in formless substance,

00:39:40.111 --> 00:39:43.651
and know that they are coming to you as fast as you can receive and use them.

00:39:44.171 --> 00:39:48.991
Nobody by cornering the visible supply can prevent you from getting what is yours.

00:39:49.971 --> 00:39:55.331
So never allow yourself to think for an instant that all the best building spots will be taken

00:39:55.331 --> 00:39:58.151
before you get ready to build your house, unless you hurry.

00:39:58.731 --> 00:40:03.151
Never worry about the trust and combines, and get anxious for fear that you will soon

00:40:03.151 --> 00:40:04.671
come to own the whole earth.

00:40:05.251 --> 00:40:09.451
Never get afraid that you will lose what you want because some other person beats you to

00:40:09.451 --> 00:40:09.791
it.

00:40:10.291 --> 00:40:11.771
That cannot possibly happen.

00:40:12.151 --> 00:40:16.451
You are not seeking anything that is possessed by anybody else, you are causing what you

00:40:16.451 --> 00:40:20.191
want to be created from formless substance, and the supply is without limits.

00:40:20.731 --> 00:40:22.471
Stick to the formulated statement.

00:40:23.351 --> 00:40:28.051
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

00:40:28.491 --> 00:40:31.751
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

00:40:32.331 --> 00:40:36.651
A thought, in this substance, produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

00:40:37.371 --> 00:40:42.351
Man can form things in his thought, and, by impressing his thought upon formless substance,

00:40:42.351 --> 00:40:45.431
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

00:41:04.885 --> 00:41:06.365
HOW RICHES COME TO YOU

00:41:07.145 --> 00:41:12.325
When I say that you do not have to drive sharp bargains, I do not mean that you do not have

00:41:12.325 --> 00:41:17.005
to drive any bargains at all, or that you are above the necessity for having any dealings

00:41:17.005 --> 00:41:18.165
with your fellow men.

00:41:18.585 --> 00:41:21.685
I mean that you will not need to deal with them unfairly.

00:41:21.685 --> 00:41:26.685
You do not have to get something for nothing, but can give to every man more than you take

00:41:26.685 --> 00:41:27.265
from him.

00:41:27.685 --> 00:41:32.305
You cannot give every man more in cash market value than you take from him, but you can

00:41:32.305 --> 00:41:36.305
give him more in use value than the cash value of the thing you take from him.

00:41:36.845 --> 00:41:41.585
The paper, ink, and other material in this book may not be worth the money you pay for

00:41:41.585 --> 00:41:41.885
it.

00:41:42.225 --> 00:41:47.345
But if the ideas suggested in it bring you thousands of dollars, you have not been wrong

00:41:47.345 --> 00:41:48.925
by those who sold it to you.

00:41:48.925 --> 00:41:52.505
They have given you a great use value for a small cash value.

00:41:53.305 --> 00:41:58.305
Let us suppose that I own a picture by one of the greatest artists, which in any civilized

00:41:58.305 --> 00:42:01.025
community is worth thousands of dollars.

00:42:01.485 --> 00:42:06.845
I take it to Baffin Bay, and by salesmanship induce an Eskimo to give a bundle of furs

00:42:06.845 --> 00:42:08.545
worth five hundred for it.

00:42:08.885 --> 00:42:12.085
I have really wronged him, for he has no use for the picture.

00:42:12.445 --> 00:42:14.125
It has no use value to him.

00:42:14.345 --> 00:42:16.045
It will not add to his life.

00:42:16.645 --> 00:42:21.005
But suppose I give him a gun worth fifty dollars for his furs.

00:42:21.745 --> 00:42:23.425
Then he has made a good bargain.

00:42:24.085 --> 00:42:25.345
He has use for the gun.

00:42:25.605 --> 00:42:28.125
It will get him many more furs and much food.

00:42:28.665 --> 00:42:30.525
It will add to his life in every day.

00:42:30.925 --> 00:42:32.125
It will make him rich.

00:42:32.945 --> 00:42:37.345
When you rise from the competitive to the creative plane, you can scan your business

00:42:37.345 --> 00:42:42.265
transactions very strictly, and if you are selling any man anything, which does not add

00:42:42.265 --> 00:42:46.785
more to his life than the thing he give you in exchange, you can afford to stop it.

00:42:47.605 --> 00:42:49.845
You do not have to beat anybody in business.

00:42:50.285 --> 00:42:54.465
And if you are in a business which does beat people, get out of it at once.

00:42:55.425 --> 00:42:59.565
Give every man more in use value than you take from him in cash value.

00:43:00.185 --> 00:43:03.665
Then you are adding to the life of the world by every business transaction.

00:43:04.685 --> 00:43:09.285
If you have people working for you, you must take from them more cash value than you pay

00:43:09.285 --> 00:43:10.065
them in wages.

00:43:10.665 --> 00:43:15.545
But you can so organize your business that it will be filled with the principle of advancement,

00:43:15.965 --> 00:43:20.305
and so that each employee who wishes to do so may advance a little every day.

00:43:20.925 --> 00:43:25.045
You can make your business do for your employees what this book is doing for you.

00:43:25.545 --> 00:43:30.065
You can so conduct your business that it will be a sort of ladder, by which every employee

00:43:30.065 --> 00:43:35.085
who will take the trouble may climb to riches himself, and given the opportunity, if he

00:43:35.085 --> 00:43:37.205
will not do so, it is not your fault.

00:43:37.865 --> 00:43:42.245
And finally, because you are to cause the creation of your riches from formless substance

00:43:42.245 --> 00:43:46.445
which permeates all your environment, it does not follow that they are to take shape from

00:43:46.445 --> 00:43:49.145
the atmosphere and come into being before your eyes.

00:43:49.965 --> 00:43:54.385
If you want a sewing machine, for instance, I do not mean to tell you that you are to

00:43:54.385 --> 00:43:58.405
impress the thought of a sewing machine on thinking substance until the machine is formed

00:43:58.405 --> 00:44:01.065
without hands, in the room where you sit or elsewhere.

00:44:01.605 --> 00:44:05.825
But if you want a sewing machine, hold the mental image of it with the most positive

00:44:05.825 --> 00:44:09.005
certainty that it is being made, or is on its way to you.

00:44:09.605 --> 00:44:14.645
After once forming the thought, have the most absolute and unquestioning faith that a sewing

00:44:14.645 --> 00:44:15.565
machine is coming.

00:44:15.965 --> 00:44:20.585
Never think of it, or speak of it, in any other way than as being sure to arrive.

00:44:20.865 --> 00:44:22.385
Claim it as already yours.

00:44:23.165 --> 00:44:27.745
It will be brought to you by the power of the supreme intelligence acting upon the minds

00:44:27.745 --> 00:44:28.365
of men.

00:44:28.785 --> 00:44:33.645
If you live in Maine, it may be that a man will be brought from Texas or Japan to engage

00:44:33.645 --> 00:44:37.305
in some transaction which will result in your getting what you want.

00:44:37.825 --> 00:44:42.865
If so, the whole matter will be as much to that man's advantage as it is to yours.

00:44:43.545 --> 00:44:48.305
Do not forget for a moment that the thinking substance is through all, in all, communicating

00:44:48.305 --> 00:44:50.425
with all, and can influence all.

00:44:50.725 --> 00:44:55.445
The desire of thinking substance for fuller life and better living has caused the creation

00:44:55.445 --> 00:45:00.345
of all the sewing machines already made, and this can cause the creation of millions more,

00:45:00.345 --> 00:45:05.605
and will, whenever men set it in motion by desire and faith, and by acting in a certain

00:45:05.605 --> 00:45:06.065
way.

00:45:06.765 --> 00:45:11.545
You can certainly have a sewing machine in your house, and it is just as certain that

00:45:11.545 --> 00:45:16.425
you can have any other thing or things which you want, and which you will use for the advancement

00:45:16.425 --> 00:45:18.665
of your own life and the lives of others.

00:45:19.405 --> 00:45:21.705
You need not hesitate about asking largely.

00:45:22.065 --> 00:45:25.465
It is your father's pleasure to give you the kingdom, said Jesus.

00:45:26.425 --> 00:45:30.805
Original substance wants to live all that is possible in you, and wants you to have

00:45:30.805 --> 00:45:34.845
all that you can or will use for the living of the most abundant life.

00:45:35.585 --> 00:45:39.945
If you fix upon your consciousness the fact that the desire you feel for the possession

00:45:39.945 --> 00:45:45.445
of riches is one with the desire for omnipotence for more complete expression, your faith becomes

00:45:45.445 --> 00:45:46.125
invincible.

00:45:47.085 --> 00:45:52.105
Once, I saw a little boy sitting at a piano, and vainly trying to bring harmony out of

00:45:52.105 --> 00:45:57.305
the keys, and I saw that he was grieved and provoked by his inability to play real music.

00:45:57.825 --> 00:46:01.065
I asked him the cause of this vexation, and he answered,

00:46:01.465 --> 00:46:05.105
I can feel the music in me, but I can't make my hands go right.

00:46:05.625 --> 00:46:10.065
The music in him was the urge of original substance, containing all the possibilities

00:46:10.065 --> 00:46:10.925
of all life.

00:46:11.305 --> 00:46:14.745
All that there is of music was seeking expression through the child.

00:46:15.465 --> 00:46:20.225
God, the one substance, is trying to live and do and enjoy things through humanity.

00:46:20.225 --> 00:46:26.485
He is saying, I want hands to build wonderful structures, to play divine harmonies, to paint

00:46:26.485 --> 00:46:27.585
glorious pictures.

00:46:28.105 --> 00:46:33.505
I want feet to run my errands, eyes to see my beauties, tongues to tell mighty truths,

00:46:33.925 --> 00:46:36.485
and to sing marvelous songs, and so on.

00:46:37.245 --> 00:46:40.705
All that there is of possibility is seeking expression through men.

00:46:41.185 --> 00:46:46.145
God wants those who can play music to have pianos and every other instrument, and to

00:46:46.145 --> 00:46:49.345
have the means to cultivate their talents to the fullest extent.

00:46:49.745 --> 00:46:53.965
He wants those who can appreciate beauty to be able to surround themselves with beautiful

00:46:53.965 --> 00:46:54.505
things.

00:46:54.925 --> 00:46:59.565
He wants those who can discern the truth to have every opportunity to travel and observe.

00:47:00.105 --> 00:47:04.445
He wants those who can appreciate dress to be beautifully clothed, and those who can

00:47:04.445 --> 00:47:07.165
appreciate good food to be luxuriously fed.

00:47:07.885 --> 00:47:12.145
He wants all these things, because it is himself that enjoys and appreciates them.

00:47:12.425 --> 00:47:17.585
It is God who wants to play, and sing, and enjoy beauty, and proclaim truth, and wear

00:47:17.585 --> 00:47:19.545
fine clothes, and eat good foods.

00:47:20.025 --> 00:47:23.925
It is God that worketh in you to will and to do, said Paul.

00:47:24.565 --> 00:47:30.245
The desire you feel for riches is the infinite seeking to express himself in you, as he sought

00:47:30.245 --> 00:47:32.965
to find expression in the little boy at the piano.

00:47:33.705 --> 00:47:35.965
So you need not hesitate to ask largely.

00:47:36.705 --> 00:47:40.085
Your part is to focalize and express the desire to God.

00:47:40.905 --> 00:47:43.205
This is a difficult point with most people.

00:47:43.205 --> 00:47:48.485
They retain something of the old idea that poverty and self-sacrifice are pleasing to

00:47:48.485 --> 00:47:48.745
God.

00:47:49.305 --> 00:47:53.285
They look upon poverty as a part of the plan, a necessity of nature.

00:47:53.965 --> 00:47:59.065
They have the idea that God has finished his work, and made all that he can make, and that

00:47:59.065 --> 00:48:03.085
the majority of men must stay poor, because there is not enough to go around.

00:48:03.645 --> 00:48:08.465
They hold so much to this erroneous thought that they feel ashamed to ask for wealth.

00:48:08.885 --> 00:48:13.625
They try not to want more than a very modest competence, just enough to make them fairly

00:48:13.625 --> 00:48:14.265
comfortable.

00:48:14.865 --> 00:48:19.885
I recall now a case of one student who was told that he must get in mind a clear picture

00:48:19.885 --> 00:48:24.665
of the things he desired, so that the creative thought of them might be impressed on formless

00:48:24.665 --> 00:48:25.265
substance.

00:48:25.765 --> 00:48:30.425
He was a very poor man, living in a rented house, and having only what he earned from

00:48:30.425 --> 00:48:34.525
day to day, and he could not grasp the fact that all wealth was his.

00:48:35.185 --> 00:48:40.765
So, after thinking the matter over, he decided that he might reasonably ask for a new rug

00:48:40.765 --> 00:48:45.985
on the floor of his best room, and an anthracite coal-stove, to heat the house during the cold

00:48:45.985 --> 00:48:46.405
winter.

00:48:46.945 --> 00:48:51.325
Following the instructions given in this book, he obtained these things in a few months,

00:48:51.625 --> 00:48:54.485
and that it dawned upon him that he had not asked enough.

00:48:54.945 --> 00:48:59.005
He went through the house in which he lived, and planned all the improvements he would

00:48:59.005 --> 00:48:59.985
like to make in it.

00:48:59.985 --> 00:49:05.125
He mentally added a bay window here, a room there, until it was complete in his mind as

00:49:05.125 --> 00:49:08.745
his ideal home, and then he planned its furnishings.

00:49:09.005 --> 00:49:13.525
Holding the whole picture in his mind, he began living in the certain way, and moving

00:49:13.525 --> 00:49:14.725
toward what he wanted.

00:49:15.165 --> 00:49:19.645
And he owns the house now, and is rebuilding it after the form of his mental image.

00:49:19.885 --> 00:49:24.225
And now, with still larger faith, he is going on to get greater things.

00:49:24.225 --> 00:49:29.765
It has been unto him according to his faith, and it is so with you and with all of us.

00:49:50.580 --> 00:49:55.300
The illustrations given in the last chapter will have conveyed to the reader the fact

00:49:55.300 --> 00:50:00.180
that the first step toward getting rich is to convey the idea of your wants to the formless

00:50:00.180 --> 00:50:00.800
substance.

00:50:01.520 --> 00:50:07.060
This is true, and you will see that in order to do so, it becomes necessary to relate yourself

00:50:07.060 --> 00:50:09.680
to the formless intelligence in a harmonious way.

00:50:10.420 --> 00:50:15.440
To secure this harmonious relation is a matter of such primary and vital importance that

00:50:15.440 --> 00:50:20.260
I shall give some space to its discussion here, and give you instructions which, if

00:50:20.260 --> 00:50:24.780
you will follow them, will be certain to bring you into perfect unity of mind with God.

00:50:25.260 --> 00:50:30.740
The whole process of mental adjustment and atonement can be summed up in one word—gratitude.

00:50:31.380 --> 00:50:35.940
First, you believe that there is one intelligent substance, from which all things proceed.

00:50:35.940 --> 00:50:40.140
Second, you believe that this substance gives you everything you desire.

00:50:40.460 --> 00:50:45.400
And third, you relate yourself to it by a feeling of deep and profound gratitude.

00:50:46.180 --> 00:50:51.520
Many people who order their lives rightly in all other ways are kept in poverty by their

00:50:51.520 --> 00:50:52.600
lack of gratitude.

00:50:53.220 --> 00:50:58.860
Having received one gift from God, they cut the wires which connect them with Him by failing

00:50:58.860 --> 00:50:59.1000
to make acknowledgement.

00:51:00.440 --> 00:51:05.600
It is easy to understand that the nearer we live to the source of wealth, the more wealth

00:51:05.600 --> 00:51:06.560
we shall receive.

00:51:06.880 --> 00:51:11.760
And it is easy also to understand that the soul that is always grateful lives in closer

00:51:11.760 --> 00:51:16.040
touch with God than the one which never looks to Him in thankful acknowledgement.

00:51:16.720 --> 00:51:21.620
The more gratefully we fix our minds on the Supreme when good things come to us, the more

00:51:21.620 --> 00:51:25.240
good things we will receive, and the more rapidly they will come.

00:51:25.500 --> 00:51:30.600
And the reason simply is that the mental attitude of gratitude draws the mind into closer touch

00:51:30.600 --> 00:51:32.740
with the source from which the blessings come.

00:51:33.440 --> 00:51:38.400
If it is a new thought to you, that gratitude brings your whole mind into closer harmony

00:51:38.400 --> 00:51:42.1000
with the creative energies of the universe, consider it well, and you will see that it

00:51:42.1000 --> 00:51:43.560
is true.

00:51:44.040 --> 00:51:48.940
The good things you already have, have come to you along the line of obedience to certain

00:51:48.940 --> 00:51:49.380
laws.

00:51:50.040 --> 00:51:54.940
Gratitude will lead your mind out along the ways by which things come, and it will keep

00:51:54.940 --> 00:51:59.560
you in close harmony with creative thought and prevent you from falling into competitive

00:51:59.560 --> 00:52:00.020
thought.

00:52:01.200 --> 00:52:05.560
Gratitude alone can keep you looking toward the All, and prevent you from falling into

00:52:05.560 --> 00:52:10.680
the error of thinking of the supply as limited, and to do that would be fatal to your hopes.

00:52:11.420 --> 00:52:16.140
There is a law of gratitude, and it is absolutely necessary that you should observe the law,

00:52:16.520 --> 00:52:18.480
if you are to get the results you seek.

00:52:19.160 --> 00:52:23.920
The law of gratitude is the natural principle that action and reaction are always equal

00:52:23.920 --> 00:52:25.520
and in opposite directions.

00:52:26.060 --> 00:52:31.820
The grateful outreaching of your mind in thankful praise to the Supreme is a liberation or expenditure

00:52:31.820 --> 00:52:32.460
of force.

00:52:32.1000 --> 00:52:38.260
It cannot fail to reach that to which it addressed, and the reaction is an instantaneous movement

00:52:38.260 --> 00:52:39.180
towards you.

00:52:39.720 --> 00:52:43.300
Draw nigh unto God, and He will draw nigh unto you.

00:52:43.740 --> 00:52:46.320
That is a statement of psychological truth.

00:52:47.040 --> 00:52:52.080
And if your gratitude is strong and constant, the reaction in formless substance will be

00:52:52.080 --> 00:52:53.280
strong and continuous.

00:52:53.800 --> 00:52:57.060
The movement of the things you want will be always toward you.

00:52:57.560 --> 00:53:01.940
Notice the grateful attitude that Jesus took, how He always seems to be saying,

00:53:02.240 --> 00:53:05.300
I thank Thee, Father, that Thou hearest me.

00:53:05.920 --> 00:53:10.880
You cannot exercise much power without gratitude, for it is gratitude that keeps you connected

00:53:10.880 --> 00:53:11.660
with power.

00:53:12.420 --> 00:53:16.660
But the value of gratitude does not consist solely in getting you more blessings in the

00:53:16.660 --> 00:53:17.080
future.

00:53:17.080 --> 00:53:22.260
Without gratitude, you cannot long keep from dissatisfied thoughts regarding things as

00:53:22.260 --> 00:53:22.900
they are.

00:53:23.280 --> 00:53:27.940
The moment you permit your mind to dwell with dissatisfaction upon things as they are, you

00:53:27.940 --> 00:53:29.100
begin to lose ground.

00:53:29.660 --> 00:53:35.480
You fix attention upon the common, the ordinary, the poor, and the squalid and mean, and your

00:53:35.480 --> 00:53:37.700
mind takes the form of these things.

00:53:38.200 --> 00:53:43.480
Then you will transmit these forms or mental images to the formless, and the common, the

00:53:43.480 --> 00:53:45.960
poor, the squalid, the mean will come to you.

00:53:45.960 --> 00:53:51.180
To permit your mind to dwell upon the inferior is to become inferior and to surround yourself

00:53:51.180 --> 00:53:52.400
with inferior things.

00:53:52.980 --> 00:53:57.340
On the other hand, to fix your attention on the best is to surround yourself with the

00:53:57.340 --> 00:53:59.020
best and to become the best.

00:53:59.580 --> 00:54:04.480
The creative power within us makes us into the image of that to which we give our attention.

00:54:05.100 --> 00:54:10.020
We are thinking substance, and thinking substance always takes the form of that to which it

00:54:10.020 --> 00:54:10.740
thinks about.

00:54:11.080 --> 00:54:14.340
The grateful mind is constantly fixed upon the best.

00:54:14.740 --> 00:54:16.740
Therefore, it tends to become the best.

00:54:16.1000 --> 00:54:20.780
It takes the form or character of the best, and will receive the best.

00:54:21.500 --> 00:54:23.920
Also, faith is born of gratitude.

00:54:24.340 --> 00:54:29.640
The grateful mind continually expects good things, and expectation becomes faith.

00:54:30.060 --> 00:54:35.260
The reaction of gratitude upon one's own mind produces faith, and every outgoing wave

00:54:35.260 --> 00:54:37.680
of grateful thanksgiving increases faith.

00:54:37.680 --> 00:54:42.860
He who has no feeling of gratitude cannot long retain a living faith, and without a

00:54:42.860 --> 00:54:48.240
living faith you cannot get rich by the creative method, as we shall see in the following chapters.

00:54:49.100 --> 00:54:53.720
It is necessary, then, to cultivate the habit of being grateful for every good thing that

00:54:53.720 --> 00:54:56.340
comes to you, and to give thanks continuously.

00:54:57.180 --> 00:55:01.820
And because all things have contributed to your advancement, you should include all things

00:55:01.820 --> 00:55:02.740
in your gratitude.

00:55:03.440 --> 00:55:08.760
Do not waste time thinking or talking about the shortcomings or wrong actions of plutocrats

00:55:08.760 --> 00:55:09.760
or trust magnets.

00:55:10.500 --> 00:55:13.400
Their organization of the world has made your opportunity.

00:55:14.060 --> 00:55:16.420
All you get really comes to you because of them.

00:55:17.020 --> 00:55:19.240
Do not rage against corrupt politicians.

00:55:19.820 --> 00:55:24.680
If it were not for politicians we should fall into anarchy, and your opportunity would be

00:55:24.680 --> 00:55:25.600
greatly lessened.

00:55:25.1000 --> 00:55:30.700
God has worked a long time and very patiently to bring us up to where we are in industry

00:55:30.700 --> 00:55:33.600
and government, and He is going right on with His work.

00:55:34.260 --> 00:55:39.700
There is not the least doubt that He will do away the plutocrats, trust magnets, captains

00:55:39.700 --> 00:55:43.280
of industry, and politicians as soon as they can be spared.

00:55:43.540 --> 00:55:46.560
But in the meantime, behold, they are all very good.

00:55:47.080 --> 00:55:51.540
Remember that they are all helping to arrange the lines of transmission along which your

00:55:51.540 --> 00:55:54.640
riches will come to you, and be grateful to them all.

00:55:55.080 --> 00:55:59.620
This will bring you into harmonious relations with the good in everything, and the good

00:55:59.620 --> 00:56:01.660
in everything will move toward you.

00:56:20.004 --> 00:56:21.564
THINKING IN THE CERTAIN WAY

00:56:22.284 --> 00:56:26.644
Turn back to chapter 6, and read again the story of the man who formed the mental image

00:56:26.644 --> 00:56:31.004
of his house, and you will get a fair idea of the initial step toward getting rich.

00:56:31.324 --> 00:56:34.784
You must form a clear and definite mental picture of what you want.

00:56:35.124 --> 00:56:38.064
You cannot transmit an idea unless you have it yourself.

00:56:38.064 --> 00:56:40.944
You must have it before you can give it.

00:56:41.244 --> 00:56:46.164
A many people fail to impress thinking substance because they have themselves only a vague

00:56:46.164 --> 00:56:49.944
and mystic concept of the things they want to do, to have, or to become.

00:56:50.624 --> 00:56:54.964
It is not enough that you should have a general desire for wealth, to do, good with.

00:56:55.404 --> 00:56:56.884
Everybody has that desire.

00:56:57.524 --> 00:57:02.164
It is not enough that you should have a wish to travel, see things, live more, etc.

00:57:02.864 --> 00:57:04.984
Everybody has those desires also.

00:57:04.984 --> 00:57:09.924
If you are going to send a wireless message to a friend, you would not send the letters

00:57:09.924 --> 00:57:14.784
of the alphabet in their order and let him construct the message for himself, nor would

00:57:14.784 --> 00:57:16.944
you take words at random from the dictionary.

00:57:17.504 --> 00:57:20.924
You would send a coherent sentence, one which meant something.

00:57:21.744 --> 00:57:26.844
When you try to impress your wants upon substance, remember that it must be done by a coherent

00:57:26.844 --> 00:57:27.424
statement.

00:57:27.804 --> 00:57:30.044
You must know what you want and be definite.

00:57:30.464 --> 00:57:35.864
You can never get rich or start a creative power into action by sending out unformed

00:57:35.864 --> 00:57:37.604
longings and vague desires.

00:57:38.624 --> 00:57:43.324
Go over your desires just as the man I have described went over his house.

00:57:43.884 --> 00:57:48.444
See just what you want and get a clear mental picture of it as you wish it to look when

00:57:48.444 --> 00:57:49.124
you get it.

00:57:49.804 --> 00:57:55.204
That clear mental picture you must have continually in mind, as the sailor has in mind a port

00:57:55.204 --> 00:57:56.944
toward which he is sailing the ship.

00:57:57.304 --> 00:57:59.824
You must keep your face toward it all the time.

00:58:00.144 --> 00:58:04.564
You must no more lose sight of it than the steersman loses sight of the compass.

00:58:05.204 --> 00:58:11.464
It is not necessary to take exercises in concentration, nor to set apart special times for prayer

00:58:11.464 --> 00:58:17.104
and affirmation, nor to go into the silence, nor to do a cold stunt of any kind.

00:58:17.664 --> 00:58:22.324
These things are well enough, but all you need is to know what you want and to want

00:58:22.324 --> 00:58:25.164
it badly enough so that it will stay in your thoughts.

00:58:25.804 --> 00:58:30.604
Spend as much your leisure time as you can in contemplating your picture, but no one

00:58:30.604 --> 00:58:34.684
needs to take exercises to concentrate his mind on a thing he really wants.

00:58:35.264 --> 00:58:39.364
It is the things you do not really care about which require effort to fix your attention

00:58:39.364 --> 00:58:40.064
upon them.

00:58:40.664 --> 00:58:45.084
And unless you really want to get rich, so that the desire is strong enough to hold your

00:58:45.084 --> 00:58:50.364
thoughts directed to the purpose as the magnetic pole holds the needle of the compass, it will

00:58:50.364 --> 00:58:54.964
hardly be worthwhile for you to try to carry out the instructions given in this book.

00:58:55.504 --> 00:59:00.384
The methods herein set forth are for people whose desire for riches is strong enough to

00:59:00.384 --> 00:59:03.964
overcome mental laziness and a love of ease, and make them work.

00:59:04.824 --> 00:59:08.704
The more clear and definite you make your picture, then, and the more you dwell upon

00:59:08.704 --> 00:59:13.644
it, bringing out all its delightful details, the stronger your desire will be.

00:59:13.964 --> 00:59:18.684
And the stronger your desire, the easier it will be to hold your mind fixed upon the picture

00:59:18.684 --> 00:59:19.644
of what you want.

00:59:20.584 --> 00:59:24.384
Something more is necessary, however, than merely to see the picture clearly.

00:59:24.984 --> 00:59:30.744
If that is all you do, you are only a dreamer, and will have little or no power for accomplishment.

00:59:31.424 --> 00:59:36.284
Behind your clear vision must be the purpose to realize it, to bring it out in tangible

00:59:36.684 --> 00:59:36.944
expression.

00:59:37.564 --> 00:59:42.644
And behind this purpose must be an invincible and unwavering faith that the thing is already

00:59:42.644 --> 00:59:47.024
yours, that it is at hand, and you have only to take possession of it.

00:59:47.584 --> 00:59:51.644
Live in the new house mentally, until it takes form around you physically.

00:59:52.324 --> 00:59:56.444
In the mental realm, enter at once into full enjoyment of the things you want.

00:59:57.384 --> 01:00:02.304
Whatsoever things ye ask for when ye pray, believe that ye receive them, and ye shall

01:00:02.304 --> 01:00:03.964
have them, said Jesus.

01:00:04.904 --> 01:00:08.844
See the things you want as if they were actually around you all the time.

01:00:09.144 --> 01:00:11.484
See yourself as owning and using them.

01:00:11.994 --> 01:00:16.144
Make use of them in imagination, just as you will use them when they are your tangible

01:00:16.144 --> 01:00:16.864
possessions.

01:00:17.524 --> 01:00:21.924
Dwell upon your mental picture until it is clear and distinct, and then take the mental

01:00:21.924 --> 01:00:24.784
attitude of ownership toward everything in that picture.

01:00:25.284 --> 01:00:29.564
Take possession of it, in mind, in the full faith that it is actually yours.

01:00:30.224 --> 01:00:31.744
Hold to this mental ownership.

01:00:32.144 --> 01:00:35.284
Do not waver for an instant in the faith that it is real.

01:00:35.884 --> 01:00:39.284
And remember what was said in the preceding chapter about gratitude.

01:00:39.284 --> 01:00:44.564
Be as thankful for it all the time as you expect it to be when it has taken form.

01:00:45.044 --> 01:00:49.864
The man who can sincerely thank God for the things which as yet he owns only in imagination,

01:00:50.304 --> 01:00:51.124
has real faith.

01:00:51.744 --> 01:00:52.824
He will get rich.

01:00:53.064 --> 01:00:55.824
He will cause the creation of whatsoever he wants.

01:00:56.704 --> 01:00:59.404
You do not need to pray repeatedly for things you want.

01:00:59.704 --> 01:01:02.344
It is not necessary to tell God about it every day.

01:01:02.964 --> 01:01:08.644
Use not vain repetitions as the heathen do, said Jesus to his pupils, for your father

01:01:08.644 --> 01:01:12.064
knoweth that ye have need of these things before ye ask him.

01:01:12.564 --> 01:01:17.004
Your part is to intelligently formulate your desire for the things which make for a larger

01:01:17.004 --> 01:01:22.684
life, and to get these desires arranged into a coherent whole, and then to impress this

01:01:22.684 --> 01:01:27.184
whole desire upon the formless substance, which has the power and the will to bring

01:01:27.184 --> 01:01:28.084
you what you want.

01:01:28.944 --> 01:01:32.244
You do not make this impression by repeating strings of words.

01:01:32.524 --> 01:01:37.904
You make it by holding the vision with unshakable purpose to attain it, and with steadfast faith

01:01:37.904 --> 01:01:39.324
that you do attain it.

01:01:39.924 --> 01:01:44.384
The answer to prayer is not according to your faith while you are talking, but according

01:01:44.384 --> 01:01:46.204
to your faith while you are working.

01:01:46.764 --> 01:01:51.264
You cannot impress the mind of God by having a special Sabbath day set apart to tell him

01:01:51.264 --> 01:01:54.584
what you want, and of forgetting him during the rest of the week.

01:01:54.984 --> 01:01:59.844
You cannot impress him by having special hours to go into your closet and pray, if you then

01:01:59.844 --> 01:02:03.424
dismiss the matter from your mind until the hour of prayer comes again.

01:02:04.064 --> 01:02:09.744
Oral prayer is well enough, and has its effect, especially upon yourself, in clarifying your

01:02:09.744 --> 01:02:11.424
vision and strengthening your faith.

01:02:12.044 --> 01:02:15.184
But it is not your oral petitions which get you what you want.

01:02:16.144 --> 01:02:19.444
In order to get rich, you do not need a sweet hour of prayer.

01:02:19.804 --> 01:02:21.424
You need to pray without ceasing.

01:02:22.004 --> 01:02:26.644
And by prayer, I mean holding steadily to your vision, with the purpose to cause its

01:02:26.644 --> 01:02:30.424
creation into solid form, and the faith that you are doing so.

01:02:31.024 --> 01:02:32.684
Believe that ye receive them.

01:02:33.284 --> 01:02:37.304
The whole matter turns on receiving, once you have clearly formed your vision.

01:02:37.944 --> 01:02:42.504
When you have formed it, it is well to make an oral statement, addressing the supreme

01:02:42.504 --> 01:02:47.844
irreverent prayer, and from that moment you must, in mind, receive what you ask for.

01:02:48.484 --> 01:02:54.064
Live in the new house, wear the fine clothes, ride in the automobile, go on the journey,

01:02:54.364 --> 01:02:56.584
and confidently plan for greater journeys.

01:02:57.284 --> 01:03:01.784
Think and speak of all the things you have asked for in terms of actual present ownership.

01:03:02.324 --> 01:03:07.204
Imagine an environment and a financial condition exactly as you want them, and live all the

01:03:07.204 --> 01:03:10.364
time in that imaginary environment and financial condition.

01:03:10.944 --> 01:03:15.424
Mind, however, that you do not do this as a mere dreamer or castle-builder.

01:03:15.844 --> 01:03:20.724
Hold to the faith that the imaginary is being realized, and to the purpose to realize it.

01:03:21.224 --> 01:03:25.924
Remember that it is faith and purpose in the use of the imagination which makes the difference

01:03:25.924 --> 01:03:28.024
between the scientist and the dreamer.

01:03:28.344 --> 01:03:32.964
And having learned this fact, it is here that you must learn the proper use of the will.

01:03:51.267 --> 01:03:52.707
HOW TO USE THE WILL

01:03:53.647 --> 01:03:58.447
To set about getting rich in a scientific way, you do not try to apply your will-power

01:03:58.447 --> 01:04:00.307
to anything outside of yourself.

01:04:00.847 --> 01:04:02.847
You have no right to do so, anyway.

01:04:03.267 --> 01:04:08.007
It is wrong to apply your will to other men and women, in order to get them to do what

01:04:08.007 --> 01:04:08.847
you wish done.

01:04:09.447 --> 01:04:15.187
It is as flagrant a wrong to coerce people by mental power as it is to coerce them by

01:04:15.187 --> 01:04:16.207
physical power.

01:04:16.707 --> 01:04:21.147
If compelling people by physical force to do things for you reduces them to slavery,

01:04:21.607 --> 01:04:24.847
compelling them by mental means accomplishes exactly the same thing.

01:04:25.247 --> 01:04:26.987
The only difference is in methods.

01:04:27.627 --> 01:04:32.887
If taking things from people by physical force is robbery, then taking things by mental force

01:04:32.887 --> 01:04:34.027
is robbery also.

01:04:34.307 --> 01:04:36.047
There is no difference in principle.

01:04:36.047 --> 01:04:41.647
You have no right to use your will-power upon another person even for his own good,

01:04:42.047 --> 01:04:44.107
for you do not know what is for his good.

01:04:44.567 --> 01:04:49.607
The science of getting rich does not require you to apply power or force to any other person

01:04:49.607 --> 01:04:50.927
in any way whatsoever.

01:04:51.487 --> 01:04:54.267
There is not the slightest necessity for doing so.

01:04:54.527 --> 01:04:59.627
Indeed, any attempt to use your will upon others will only tend to defeat your purpose.

01:05:00.207 --> 01:05:04.727
You do not need to apply your will to things in order to compel them to come to you.

01:05:05.227 --> 01:05:10.107
That would simply be trying to coerce God and would be foolish and useless as well as

01:05:10.107 --> 01:05:10.967
irreverent.

01:05:11.627 --> 01:05:15.947
You do not have to compel God to give you good things any more than you have to use

01:05:15.947 --> 01:05:18.107
your will-power to make the sun rise.

01:05:18.547 --> 01:05:23.447
You do not have to use your will-power to conquer an unfriendly deity or to make stubborn

01:05:23.447 --> 01:05:25.727
and rebellious forces do your bidding.

01:05:26.727 --> 01:05:31.107
Substance is friendly to you and is more anxious to give you what you want than you are to

01:05:31.107 --> 01:05:31.627
get it.

01:05:32.167 --> 01:05:35.747
To get rich, you need only to use your will-power upon yourself.

01:05:36.367 --> 01:05:41.167
When you know what to think or do, then you must use your will to compel yourself to think

01:05:41.167 --> 01:05:42.787
and do the right things.

01:05:43.227 --> 01:05:47.667
That is the legitimate use of the will in getting what you want, to use it in holding

01:05:47.667 --> 01:05:49.227
yourself to the right course.

01:05:49.847 --> 01:05:53.447
Use your will to keep yourself thinking and acting in a certain way.

01:05:54.167 --> 01:06:00.307
Do not try to project your will or your thoughts or your mind out into space, to act on things

01:06:00.307 --> 01:06:01.007
or people.

01:06:01.887 --> 01:06:05.827
Keep your mind at home, it can accomplish more there than elsewhere.

01:06:06.907 --> 01:06:11.707
Use your mind to form a mental image of what you want, and to hold that vision with faith

01:06:11.707 --> 01:06:16.227
and purpose, and use your will to keep your mind working in the right way.

01:06:16.887 --> 01:06:21.307
The more steady and continuous your faith and purpose, the more rapidly you will get

01:06:21.307 --> 01:06:26.547
rich, because you will make only positive impressions upon substance, and you will not

01:06:26.547 --> 01:06:29.507
neutralize or offset them by negative impressions.

01:06:30.287 --> 01:06:35.287
The picture of your desires, held with faith and purpose, is taken up by the formless,

01:06:35.547 --> 01:06:39.587
and permits it to great distances throughout the universe for all I know.

01:06:40.327 --> 01:06:44.887
As this impression spreads, all things are set moving toward its realization.

01:06:45.447 --> 01:06:50.787
Every living thing, every inanimate thing, and the things yet uncreated, are stirred

01:06:50.787 --> 01:06:53.327
toward bringing into being that which you want.

01:06:53.807 --> 01:06:59.247
All force begins to be exerted in that direction, all things begin to move toward you.

01:06:59.787 --> 01:07:04.907
The minds of people, everywhere, are influenced toward doing the things necessary to the fulfilling

01:07:04.907 --> 01:07:07.967
of your desires, and they work for you unconsciously.

01:07:08.387 --> 01:07:12.387
But you can check all this by starting a negative impression in the formless substance.

01:07:12.867 --> 01:07:17.787
Doubt or unbelief is as certain to start a movement away from you, as faith and purpose

01:07:17.787 --> 01:07:19.507
are to start one toward you.

01:07:19.967 --> 01:07:25.087
It is by not understanding this, that most people who try to make use of mental science

01:07:25.087 --> 01:07:26.987
in getting rich make their failure.

01:07:27.407 --> 01:07:32.387
Every hour and moment you spend in giving heed to doubts and fears, every hour you spend

01:07:32.387 --> 01:07:37.647
in worry, every hour in which your soul is possessed by unbelief, sets a current away

01:07:37.647 --> 01:07:40.647
from you, into a whole domain of intelligent substance.

01:07:41.147 --> 01:07:45.107
All the promises are unto them that believe, and unto them only.

01:07:45.627 --> 01:07:51.167
Notice how insistent Jesus was upon his point of belief, and now you know the reason why.

01:07:51.867 --> 01:07:56.727
Since belief is all-important, it behooves you to guard your thoughts, and as your beliefs

01:07:56.727 --> 01:08:01.387
will be shaped in a very great extent by the things you observe and think about, it is

01:08:01.387 --> 01:08:03.387
important that you should command your attention.

01:08:04.067 --> 01:08:08.947
And here the will comes into use, for it is by your will that you determine upon what

01:08:08.947 --> 01:08:10.687
things your attention shall be fixed.

01:08:10.687 --> 01:08:14.787
If you want to become rich, you must not make a study of poverty.

01:08:15.527 --> 01:08:19.187
Things are not brought into being by thinking about their opposites.

01:08:19.467 --> 01:08:23.487
Health is never to be attained by studying disease and thinking about disease.

01:08:24.267 --> 01:08:28.187
Righteousness is not to be promoted by studying sin and thinking about sin.

01:08:28.447 --> 01:08:32.267
And no one ever got rich by studying poverty and thinking about poverty.

01:08:33.167 --> 01:08:38.647
Medicine as a science of disease has increased disease, religion as science of sin has promoted

01:08:38.647 --> 01:08:43.627
and economics as a study of poverty will fill the world with wretchedness and want.

01:08:44.447 --> 01:08:48.847
Do not talk about poverty, do not investigate it or concern yourself with it.

01:08:49.247 --> 01:08:51.187
Never mind what its causes are.

01:08:51.527 --> 01:08:52.927
You have nothing to do with them.

01:08:53.447 --> 01:08:55.167
What concerns you is the cure.

01:08:56.107 --> 01:08:59.347
Do not spend your time in charitable work or charity movements.

01:08:59.867 --> 01:09:03.887
All charity only tends to perpetuate the wretchedness it aims to eradicate.

01:09:04.387 --> 01:09:09.707
I do not say that you should be hard-hearted or unkind and refuse to hear the cry of need.

01:09:10.187 --> 01:09:14.387
But you must not try to eradicate poverty in any of the conventional ways.

01:09:14.887 --> 01:09:19.707
Put poverty behind you and put all that pertains to it behind you and make good.

01:09:20.287 --> 01:09:23.027
Get rich, that is the best way you can help the poor.

01:09:23.567 --> 01:09:28.087
And you cannot hold a mental image which is to make you rich if you fill your mind with

01:09:28.087 --> 01:09:29.207
pictures of poverty.

01:09:29.767 --> 01:09:33.707
Do not read books or papers which give you circumstantial accounts of the wretchedness

01:09:33.707 --> 01:09:37.647
of the tenement dwellers, of the horrors of child labor and so on.

01:09:38.067 --> 01:09:42.487
Do not read anything which fills your mind with gloomy images of want and suffering.

01:09:43.087 --> 01:09:47.667
You cannot help the poor in the least by knowing about these things, and the widespread knowledge

01:09:47.667 --> 01:09:50.567
of them does not tend to all to do away with poverty.

01:09:51.187 --> 01:09:55.487
What tends to do away with poverty is not the getting of pictures of poverty into your

01:09:55.487 --> 01:09:58.767
mind, but getting pictures of wealth into the minds of the poor.

01:09:59.207 --> 01:10:03.687
You are not deserting the poor in their misery when you refuse to allow your mind to be filled

01:10:03.687 --> 01:10:05.227
with pictures of that misery.

01:10:06.007 --> 01:10:11.147
Poverty can be done away with not by increasing the number of well-to-do people to think about

01:10:11.147 --> 01:10:16.567
poverty, but by increasing the number of poor people who purpose with faith to get rich.

01:10:17.307 --> 01:10:20.347
The poor do not need charity, they need inspiration.

01:10:20.767 --> 01:10:24.947
Charity only sends them a loaf of bread to keep them alive in their wretchedness, or

01:10:24.947 --> 01:10:30.147
gives them an entertainment to make them forget for an hour or two, but inspiration will cause

01:10:30.147 --> 01:10:31.847
them to rise out of their misery.

01:10:32.307 --> 01:10:36.567
If you want to help the poor, demonstrate to them that they can become rich.

01:10:36.927 --> 01:10:38.567
Prove it by getting rich yourself.

01:10:39.467 --> 01:10:43.807
The only way in which poverty will ever be banished from this world is by getting a large

01:10:43.807 --> 01:10:47.727
and constantly increasing number of people to practice the teaching of this book.

01:10:48.407 --> 01:10:52.467
People must be taught to become rich by creation, not by competition.

01:10:53.647 --> 01:10:58.247
Every man who becomes rich by competition throws down behind him the ladder by which

01:10:58.247 --> 01:11:03.887
he rises and keeps others down, but every man who gets rich by creation opens a way

01:11:03.887 --> 01:11:07.187
for thousands to follow him and inspires them to do so.

01:11:07.607 --> 01:11:12.487
You are not showing hardness of heart or an unfeeling disposition when you refuse to pity

01:11:12.487 --> 01:11:18.307
poverty, see poverty, read about poverty, or think and talk about it, or to listen to

01:11:18.307 --> 01:11:20.127
those who do talk about it.

01:11:20.567 --> 01:11:25.327
Use your will-power to keep your mind off the subject of poverty and to keep it fixed

01:11:25.327 --> 01:11:28.387
with faith and purpose on the vision of what you want.

01:11:49.252 --> 01:11:53.472
You cannot retain a true and clear vision of wealth if you are constantly turning your

01:11:53.472 --> 01:11:57.612
attention to opposing pictures, whether they be external or imaginary.

01:11:58.532 --> 01:12:03.632
To not tell of your past troubles of a financial nature, if you have had them, do not think

01:12:03.632 --> 01:12:04.392
of them at all.

01:12:04.392 --> 01:12:08.912
Do not tell of the poverty of your parents, or the hardships of your early life.

01:12:09.392 --> 01:12:13.992
To do any of these things is to mentally class yourself with the poor for the time being,

01:12:14.412 --> 01:12:17.672
and it will certainly check the movement of things in your direction.

01:12:18.292 --> 01:12:21.452
Let the dead bury their dead, as Jesus said.

01:12:22.072 --> 01:12:26.212
Put poverty and all things that pertain to poverty completely behind you.

01:12:26.532 --> 01:12:31.052
You have accepted a certain theory of the universe as being correct, and are resting

01:12:31.052 --> 01:12:33.612
all your hopes of happiness on its being correct.

01:12:33.972 --> 01:12:37.092
And what can you gain by giving heed to conflicting theories?

01:12:37.952 --> 01:12:42.372
Do not read religious books which tell you that the world is soon coming to an end.

01:12:42.812 --> 01:12:47.512
And do not read the writing of muckrackers and pessimistic philosophers who tell you

01:12:47.512 --> 01:12:48.792
that it is going to the devil.

01:12:49.632 --> 01:12:52.532
The world is not going to the devil, it is going to God.

01:12:53.012 --> 01:12:54.332
It is wonderful becoming.

01:12:55.012 --> 01:13:00.112
True, there may be a good many things in existing conditions which are disagreeable, but what

01:13:00.112 --> 01:13:04.172
is the use of studying them when they are certainly passing away, and when the study

01:13:04.172 --> 01:13:07.372
of them only tends to check their passing and keep them with us?

01:13:07.732 --> 01:13:12.312
Why give time and attention to things which are being removed by evolutionary growth,

01:13:12.452 --> 01:13:16.872
when you can hasten their removal only by promoting the evolutionary growth as far as

01:13:16.872 --> 01:13:18.012
your part of it goes?

01:13:18.632 --> 01:13:23.072
No matter how horrible and seeming may be the conditions in certain countries, sections

01:13:23.072 --> 01:13:27.812
or places, you waste your time and destroy your own chances by considering them.

01:13:28.432 --> 01:13:31.412
You should interest yourself in the world's becoming rich.

01:13:32.532 --> 01:13:37.332
Think of the riches the world is coming into, instead of the poverty it is growing out of.

01:13:37.932 --> 01:13:42.552
And bear in mind that the only way in which you can assist the world in growing rich is

01:13:42.552 --> 01:13:47.012
by growing rich yourself through the creative method, not the competitive one.

01:13:47.432 --> 01:13:50.772
Give your attention wholly to the riches, ignore poverty.

01:13:51.772 --> 01:13:56.532
Whenever you think or speak of those who are poor, think and speak of them as those who

01:13:56.532 --> 01:14:02.132
are becoming rich, as those who are to be congratulated rather than pitied, then they

01:14:02.132 --> 01:14:06.312
and others will catch the inspiration and begin to search for the way out.

01:14:06.972 --> 01:14:11.892
Because I say that you are to give your whole time and mind and thought to riches, it does

01:14:11.892 --> 01:14:14.372
not follow that you are to be sordid or mean.

01:14:15.052 --> 01:14:19.792
To become really rich is the noblest aim you can have in life, for it includes everything

01:14:19.792 --> 01:14:20.292
else.

01:14:20.812 --> 01:14:25.852
On the competitive plane, the struggle to get rich is a godless scramble for power over

01:14:25.852 --> 01:14:30.152
the other man, but when we come into the creative mind, all this is changed.

01:14:30.752 --> 01:14:35.352
All that is possible in the way of greatness and soul-enfoldment, of service and love the

01:14:35.352 --> 01:14:37.612
endeavor comes by way of getting rich.

01:14:38.172 --> 01:14:40.372
All is made possible by the use of things.

01:14:41.052 --> 01:14:45.832
If you lack for physical health, you will find that the attainment of it is conditional

01:14:45.832 --> 01:14:47.012
on your getting rich.

01:14:47.792 --> 01:14:52.692
Only those who are emancipated from financial worry and who have the means to live a carefree

01:14:52.692 --> 01:14:56.892
existence and follow hygienic practices can have and retain health.

01:14:57.572 --> 01:15:02.012
Moral and spiritual greatness is possible only to those who are above the competitive

01:15:02.012 --> 01:15:06.832
battle of existence, and only those who are becoming rich on the plane of creative thought

01:15:06.832 --> 01:15:09.632
are free from the degrading influences of competition.

01:15:10.252 --> 01:15:14.952
If your heart is set on domestic happiness, remember that love flourishes best where there

01:15:14.952 --> 01:15:20.632
is refinement, a high level of thought, and freedom from corrupting influences, and these

01:15:20.632 --> 01:15:25.112
are to be found only where riches are attained by the exercise of creative thought without

01:15:25.112 --> 01:15:26.472
strife or rivalry.

01:15:27.292 --> 01:15:32.112
You can aim at nothing so great or noble, I repeat, as to become rich, and you must

01:15:32.112 --> 01:15:36.672
fix your attention upon your mental picture of riches to the exclusion of all that may

01:15:36.672 --> 01:15:38.472
tend to dim or obscure the vision.

01:15:39.092 --> 01:15:42.452
You must learn to see the underlying truth in all things.

01:15:42.712 --> 01:15:48.252
You must see beneath all seemingly wrong conditions the great one life ever moving forward toward

01:15:48.252 --> 01:15:50.732
fuller expression and more complete happiness.

01:15:51.552 --> 01:15:56.192
It is the truth that there is no such thing as poverty, that there is only wealth.

01:15:56.912 --> 01:16:01.252
Some people remain in poverty because they are ignorant of the fact that there is wealth

01:16:01.252 --> 01:16:05.592
for them, and these can be best taught by showing them the way of affluence in your

01:16:05.592 --> 01:16:06.892
own person and practice.

01:16:07.492 --> 01:16:12.532
Others are poor because, while they feel that there is a way out, they are too intellectually

01:16:12.532 --> 01:16:18.232
indolent to put forth the mental effort necessary to find that way and by travel it, and for

01:16:18.232 --> 01:16:23.172
these the very best thing you can do is to arouse their desire by showing them the happiness

01:16:23.172 --> 01:16:24.932
that comes from being rightly rich.

01:16:25.932 --> 01:16:30.632
Others still are poor because, while they have some notion of science, they have become

01:16:30.632 --> 01:16:35.692
so swamped and lost in the maze of metaphysical and occult theories that they do not know

01:16:35.692 --> 01:16:36.752
which road to take.

01:16:37.052 --> 01:16:40.392
They try a mixture of many systems and fail in all.

01:16:40.812 --> 01:16:45.472
For these again the very best thing to do is to show the right way in your own person

01:16:46.052 --> 01:16:49.892
An ounce of doing things is worth a pound of theorizing.

01:16:50.712 --> 01:16:54.932
The very best thing you can do for the whole world is to make the most of yourself.

01:16:55.632 --> 01:17:00.692
You can serve God and man in no more effective way than by getting rich, that is, if you

01:17:00.692 --> 01:17:04.092
get rich by the creative method and not by the competitive one.

01:17:04.812 --> 01:17:09.412
Another thing, we assert that this book gives in detail the principles of the science of

01:17:09.412 --> 01:17:14.372
getting rich, and if that is true, you do not need to read any other book upon the subject.

01:17:14.372 --> 01:17:19.992
This may sound narrow and egoistical, but consider, there is no more scientific method

01:17:19.992 --> 01:17:25.352
of computation in mathematics than by addition, subtraction, multiplication and division.

01:17:25.932 --> 01:17:27.412
No other method is possible.

01:17:27.872 --> 01:17:30.832
There can be but one shortest distance between two points.

01:17:31.372 --> 01:17:36.292
There is only one way to think scientifically, and that is to think in the way that leads

01:17:36.292 --> 01:17:38.692
to the most direct and simple route to the goal.

01:17:39.252 --> 01:17:45.312
No man has yet formulated a briefer or less complex system than the one set forth herein.

01:17:45.592 --> 01:17:48.172
It has been stripped of all non-essentials.

01:17:48.432 --> 01:17:53.632
When you commence on this, lay all others aside, put them out of your mind altogether.

01:17:54.292 --> 01:17:59.532
Read this book every day, keep it with you, commit it to memory, and do not think about

01:17:59.532 --> 01:18:01.052
other systems and theories.

01:18:01.452 --> 01:18:06.732
If you do, you will begin to have doubts, and to be uncertain and wavering in your thought,

01:18:06.732 --> 01:18:09.252
and then you will begin to make failures.

01:18:10.092 --> 01:18:14.712
After you have made good and become rich, you may study other systems as much as you

01:18:14.712 --> 01:18:19.092
please, but until you are quite sure that you have gained what you want, do not read

01:18:19.092 --> 01:18:23.912
anything on this line but this book, unless it be the authors mentioned in the preface,

01:18:24.652 --> 01:18:29.812
and read only the most optimistic comments on the word's news, those in harmony with

01:18:29.812 --> 01:18:30.532
your picture.

01:18:31.392 --> 01:18:34.592
Also, postpone your investigations into the occult.

01:18:34.892 --> 01:18:39.132
Do not dabble in theosophy, spiritualism, or kindred studies.

01:18:39.612 --> 01:18:44.792
It is very likely that the dead still live and are near, but if they are, let them alone.

01:18:45.172 --> 01:18:46.292
Mind your own business.

01:18:47.052 --> 01:18:52.172
Wherever the spirits of the dead may be, they have their own work to do, and their own problems

01:18:52.172 --> 01:18:55.332
to solve, and we have no right to interfere with them.

01:18:55.692 --> 01:18:59.952
We cannot help them, and it is very doubtful whether they can help us, or whether we have

01:18:59.952 --> 01:19:02.952
any right to trespass upon their time if they can.

01:19:03.632 --> 01:19:08.132
Let the dead and the hereafter alone, and solve your own problem, get rich.

01:19:08.672 --> 01:19:13.452
If you begin to mix with the occult, you will start mental cross-currents, which will surely

01:19:13.452 --> 01:19:15.112
bring your hopes to shipwreck.

01:19:15.472 --> 01:19:20.092
Now, this and the preceding chapters have brought us to the following statement of the

01:19:20.092 --> 01:19:20.852
basic facts.

01:19:21.752 --> 01:19:26.612
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

01:19:26.612 --> 01:19:30.512
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

01:19:31.212 --> 01:19:35.472
A thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

01:19:36.352 --> 01:19:41.172
Man can form things in his thought, and, by impressing his thought upon former substance,

01:19:41.552 --> 01:19:44.292
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

01:19:44.852 --> 01:19:49.472
In order to do this, man must pass from the competitive to the creative mind.

01:19:49.852 --> 01:19:54.112
He must form a clear mental picture of the things he wants, and hold this picture in

01:19:54.112 --> 01:19:59.032
thoughts with the fixed purpose to get what he wants, and the unwavering faith that he

01:19:59.032 --> 01:20:04.192
does get what he wants, closing his mind against all that may tend to shake his purpose, dim

01:20:04.192 --> 01:20:06.272
his vision, or quench his faith.

01:20:06.692 --> 01:20:11.672
And in addition to all this, we shall now see that he must live and act in a certain

01:20:11.672 --> 01:20:12.092
way.

01:20:31.598 --> 01:20:33.498
ACTING IN A CERTAIN WAY

01:20:33.498 --> 01:20:38.538
Thought is the creative power, or the impelling force which causes the creative power to act.

01:20:39.018 --> 01:20:43.738
Thinking in a certain way will bring riches to you, but you must not rely upon thought

01:20:43.738 --> 01:20:46.558
alone, paying no attention to personal action.

01:20:47.338 --> 01:20:52.398
That is the rock upon which many otherwise scientific metaphysical thinkers meet shipwreck,

01:20:52.678 --> 01:20:55.498
the failure to connect thought with personal action.

01:20:56.178 --> 01:21:01.378
We have not yet reached a stage of development, even supposing such a stage to be possible,

01:21:01.838 --> 01:21:06.778
in which man can create directly from form a substance without nature's processes or

01:21:06.778 --> 01:21:08.038
the work of human hands.

01:21:08.658 --> 01:21:12.998
Man must not only think, but his personal action must supplement his thought.

01:21:13.758 --> 01:21:18.658
By thought you can cause the gold in the hearts of the mountains to be impelled toward you,

01:21:18.858 --> 01:21:24.778
but it will not mine itself, refine itself, coin itself into double eagles, and come rolling

01:21:24.778 --> 01:21:27.418
along the roads seeking its way into your pocket.

01:21:28.178 --> 01:21:33.618
Under the impelling power of the Supreme Spirit, man's affairs will be so ordered that someone

01:21:33.618 --> 01:21:39.118
will be led to mine the gold for you, other man's business transactions will be so directed

01:21:39.118 --> 01:21:43.498
that the gold will be brought toward you, and you must so arrange your own business

01:21:43.498 --> 01:21:47.098
affairs that you may be able to receive it when it comes to you.

01:21:47.618 --> 01:21:53.018
Your thought makes all things, animate and inanimate, work to bring you what you want,

01:21:53.398 --> 01:21:57.858
but your personal activity must be such that you can rightly receive what you want when

01:21:57.858 --> 01:21:58.738
it reaches you.

01:21:59.258 --> 01:22:02.438
You are not to take it as charity, nor to steal it.

01:22:02.658 --> 01:22:06.938
You must give every man more in news value than he gives you in cash value.

01:22:07.478 --> 01:22:12.198
The scientific use of thought consists in forming a clear and distinct mental image

01:22:12.198 --> 01:22:17.658
of what you want, in holding fast to the purpose to get what you want, and in realizing with

01:22:17.658 --> 01:22:20.138
grateful faith that you do get what you want.

01:22:20.858 --> 01:22:26.278
Do not try to project your thought in any mysterious or occult way with the idea of

01:22:26.278 --> 01:22:28.658
having it go out and do things for you.

01:22:28.798 --> 01:22:32.518
That is wasted effort, and will weaken your power to think with sanity.

01:22:33.178 --> 01:22:37.458
The action of thought in getting rich is fully explained in the preceding chapters.

01:22:37.938 --> 01:22:42.558
Your faith and purpose positively impress your vision upon formless substance, which

01:22:42.558 --> 01:22:45.218
has the same desire for more life that you have.

01:22:45.518 --> 01:22:50.118
And this vision, received from you, sets all the creative forces at work in and through

01:22:50.118 --> 01:22:53.578
their regular channels of action, but direct it toward you.

01:22:53.858 --> 01:22:57.398
It is not your part to guide or supervise the creative process.

01:22:57.718 --> 01:23:02.438
All you have to do with that is to retain your vision, stick to your purpose, and maintain

01:23:02.438 --> 01:23:03.838
your faith and gratitude.

01:23:04.778 --> 01:23:09.258
But you must act in a certain way, so that you can appropriate what is yours when it

01:23:09.258 --> 01:23:13.798
comes to you, so that you can meet the things you have in your picture, and put them in

01:23:13.798 --> 01:23:15.778
their proper places as they arrive.

01:23:16.258 --> 01:23:18.118
You can really see the truth of this.

01:23:18.518 --> 01:23:23.378
When things reach you, they will be in the hands of other men, who will ask an equivalent

01:23:23.378 --> 01:23:24.098
for them.

01:23:24.438 --> 01:23:28.358
And you can only get what is yours by giving the other man what is his.

01:23:28.938 --> 01:23:33.478
Your pocket-book is not going to be transformed into a fortune not dispersed, which shall

01:23:33.478 --> 01:23:36.178
be always full of money without effort on your part.

01:23:36.698 --> 01:23:39.238
This is a crucial point in the science of getting rich.

01:23:39.578 --> 01:23:44.418
Right here, when thought and personal action must be combined, there are very many people

01:23:44.418 --> 01:23:49.158
who, consciously or unconsciously, set the creative forces in action by the strength

01:23:49.158 --> 01:23:54.158
and persistence of their desires, but who remain poor, because they do not provide for

01:23:54.158 --> 01:23:56.598
the reception of the thing they want when it comes.

01:23:57.138 --> 01:24:01.998
By thought, the thing you want is brought to you, by action you receive it.

01:24:02.778 --> 01:24:06.758
Whatever your action is to be, it is evident that you must act now.

01:24:07.278 --> 01:24:12.138
You cannot act in the past, and it is essential to the clearness of your mental vision that

01:24:12.138 --> 01:24:14.058
you dismiss the past from your mind.

01:24:14.498 --> 01:24:17.818
You cannot act in the future, for the future is not here yet.

01:24:18.318 --> 01:24:23.698
And you cannot tell how you will want to act in any future contingency until that contingency

01:24:23.698 --> 01:24:24.478
has arrived.

01:24:24.478 --> 01:24:29.338
Because you are not in the right business, or the right environment now, do not think

01:24:29.338 --> 01:24:34.098
that you must postpone action until you get into the right business or environment, and

01:24:34.098 --> 01:24:39.318
do not spend time in the present taking thought as to the best course in possible future emergencies.

01:24:40.118 --> 01:24:43.578
Have faith in your ability to meet any emergency when it arrives.

01:24:44.478 --> 01:24:49.038
If you act in the present with your mind on the future, your present action will be with

01:24:49.038 --> 01:24:51.458
a divided mind, and will not be effective.

01:24:51.978 --> 01:24:54.478
Put your whole mind into present action.

01:24:55.298 --> 01:24:59.898
Do not give your creative impulse to your original substance, and then sit down and

01:24:59.898 --> 01:25:00.878
wait for results.

01:25:01.278 --> 01:25:03.338
If you do, you will never get them.

01:25:03.758 --> 01:25:04.578
Act now.

01:25:04.998 --> 01:25:09.338
There is never any time but now, and there never will be any time but now.

01:25:09.878 --> 01:25:14.258
If you are ever to begin to make ready for the reception of what you want, you must begin

01:25:14.258 --> 01:25:14.698
now.

01:25:15.258 --> 01:25:20.638
And your action, whatever it is, must most likely be in your present business or employment,

01:25:20.638 --> 01:25:24.298
and must be upon the persons and things in your present environment.

01:25:24.918 --> 01:25:26.738
You cannot act where you are not.

01:25:27.158 --> 01:25:28.698
You cannot act where you have been.

01:25:29.118 --> 01:25:31.118
And you cannot act where you are going to be.

01:25:31.538 --> 01:25:33.398
You can act only where you are.

01:25:34.218 --> 01:25:37.998
Do not bother as to whether yesterday's work was well done or ill done.

01:25:38.178 --> 01:25:39.638
Do today's work well.

01:25:40.218 --> 01:25:42.338
Do not try to do tomorrow's work now.

01:25:42.778 --> 01:25:45.618
There will be plenty of time to do that when you get to it.

01:25:46.138 --> 01:25:51.418
Do not try, by occult or mystical means, to act on people or things that are out of your

01:25:51.418 --> 01:25:51.778
reach.

01:25:52.498 --> 01:25:55.398
Do not wait for a change of environment before you act.

01:25:55.818 --> 01:25:58.018
Get a change of environment by action.

01:25:58.698 --> 01:26:03.698
You can so act upon the environment in which you are now, as to cause yourself to be transferred

01:26:03.698 --> 01:26:04.978
to a better environment.

01:26:05.738 --> 01:26:10.198
Hold with faith and purpose the vision of yourself in the better environment, but act

01:26:10.198 --> 01:26:14.558
upon your present environment with all your heart, and with all your strength, and with

01:26:14.558 --> 01:26:15.338
all your mind.

01:26:16.078 --> 01:26:19.078
Do not spend any time in daydreaming or castle building.

01:26:19.818 --> 01:26:22.938
Hold to the one vision of what you want, and act now.

01:26:23.698 --> 01:26:29.158
Do not cast about seeking some new thing to do, or some strange, unusual, or remarkable

01:26:29.158 --> 01:26:31.938
action to perform as a first step toward getting rich.

01:26:32.418 --> 01:26:37.098
It is probable that your actions, at least for some time to come, will be those you have

01:26:37.098 --> 01:26:39.098
been performing for some time past.

01:26:39.258 --> 01:26:43.978
But you are to begin now to perform these actions in a certain way, which will surely

01:26:43.978 --> 01:26:45.038
make you rich.

01:26:45.438 --> 01:26:50.738
If you are engaged in some business, and feel that it is not the right one for you, do not

01:26:50.738 --> 01:26:54.058
wait until you get into the right business before you begin to act.

01:26:54.498 --> 01:26:58.778
Do not feel discouraged, or sit down and lament because you are misplaced.

01:26:59.218 --> 01:27:04.138
No man was ever so misplaced, but that he could not find the right place, and no man

01:27:04.138 --> 01:27:08.758
ever became so involved in the wrong business, but that he could get into the right business.

01:27:09.358 --> 01:27:14.498
Hold the vision of yourself in the right business, with the purpose to get into it, and the faith

01:27:14.498 --> 01:27:19.578
that you will get into it, and are getting into it, but act in your present business.

01:27:20.278 --> 01:27:24.458
Use your present business as the means of getting a better one, and use your present

01:27:24.458 --> 01:27:27.518
environment as the means of getting into a better one.

01:27:28.058 --> 01:27:32.658
Your vision of the right business, if held with faith and purpose, will cause the Supreme

01:27:32.658 --> 01:27:37.478
to move the right business toward you, and your action, if performed in a certain way,

01:27:37.478 --> 01:27:39.858
will cause you to move toward the business.

01:27:40.538 --> 01:27:45.578
If you are an employee, or wage earner, and feel that you must change places in order

01:27:45.578 --> 01:27:50.478
to get what you want, do not project your thought into space and rely upon it to get

01:27:50.478 --> 01:27:53.498
you another job, it will probably fail to do so.

01:27:54.218 --> 01:27:58.598
Hold the vision of yourself in the job you want, while you act with faith and purpose

01:27:58.598 --> 01:28:02.118
on the job you have, and you will certainly get the job you want.

01:28:02.748 --> 01:28:07.538
Your vision and faith will set the creative force in motion to bring it toward you, and

01:28:07.538 --> 01:28:11.718
your action will cause the forces in your own environment to move you toward the place

01:28:11.718 --> 01:28:12.238
you want.

01:28:12.658 --> 01:28:16.498
In closing this chapter, we will add another statement to our syllabus.

01:28:17.098 --> 01:28:22.058
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

01:28:22.878 --> 01:28:26.058
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

01:28:26.798 --> 01:28:31.198
A thought, in this substance, produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

01:28:31.798 --> 01:28:36.898
Man can form things in his thought, and, by impressing his thought upon formless substance,

01:28:37.198 --> 01:28:39.918
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

01:28:40.438 --> 01:28:44.778
In order to do this, man must pass from the competitive to the creative mind.

01:28:45.138 --> 01:28:49.918
He must form a clear mental picture of the thing he wants, and hold this picture in his

01:28:49.918 --> 01:28:54.438
thoughts, with the fixed purpose to get what he wants, and the unwavering faith that he

01:28:54.438 --> 01:28:59.358
does get what he wants, closing his mind to all that may tend to shake his purpose, dim

01:28:59.358 --> 01:29:01.278
his vision, or quench his faith.

01:29:01.678 --> 01:29:06.578
That he may receive what he wants when it comes, man must act now upon the people and

01:29:06.578 --> 01:29:08.398
things in his present environment.

01:29:27.318 --> 01:29:28.578
EFFICIENT ACTION.

01:29:29.518 --> 01:29:34.078
You must use your thought as directed in previous chapters, and begin to do what you can do

01:29:34.078 --> 01:29:37.478
where you are, and you must do all that you can do where you are.

01:29:38.138 --> 01:29:43.078
You can advance only by being larger than your present place, and no man is larger than

01:29:43.078 --> 01:29:47.198
his present place, who leaves undone any of the work pertaining to that place.

01:29:47.938 --> 01:29:52.358
The world is advanced only by those who more than fill their present places.

01:29:52.998 --> 01:29:57.878
If no man quite filled his present place, you can see that there must be a going backward

01:29:57.878 --> 01:29:58.658
in everything.

01:29:59.298 --> 01:30:04.678
Those who do not quite fill their places are dead with bond society, government, commerce,

01:30:04.878 --> 01:30:05.618
and industry.

01:30:05.958 --> 01:30:09.098
They must be carried along by others at a great expense.

01:30:09.518 --> 01:30:14.198
The progress of the world is retarded only by those who do not fill the places they are

01:30:14.198 --> 01:30:14.538
holding.

01:30:14.978 --> 01:30:20.618
They belong to a former age and a lower stage or plane of life, and their tendency is toward

01:30:20.618 --> 01:30:21.378
degeneration.

01:30:21.978 --> 01:30:25.598
No society could advance if every man was smaller than his place.

01:30:26.158 --> 01:30:30.018
Social evolution is guided by the law of physical and mental evolution.

01:30:30.438 --> 01:30:34.058
In the animal world, evolution is caused by excess of life.

01:30:34.058 --> 01:30:39.118
When an organism has more life than can be expressed in the functions of its own plane,

01:30:39.358 --> 01:30:43.918
it develops the organs of a higher plane, and a new species is originated.

01:30:44.778 --> 01:30:49.638
There never would have been new species had there not been organisms which more than filled

01:30:49.638 --> 01:30:50.418
their places.

01:30:50.958 --> 01:30:52.938
The law is exactly the same for you.

01:30:53.198 --> 01:30:57.358
Your getting rich depends upon your applying this principle to your own affairs.

01:30:58.038 --> 01:31:03.218
Every day is either a successful day or a day of failure, and it is the successful days

01:31:03.218 --> 01:31:04.558
which get you what you want.

01:31:05.138 --> 01:31:10.598
If every day is a failure, you can never get rich, while if every day is a success, you

01:31:10.598 --> 01:31:12.178
cannot fail to get rich.

01:31:12.618 --> 01:31:17.578
If there is something that may be done today, and you do not do it, you have failed in so

01:31:17.578 --> 01:31:23.278
far as that thing is concerned, and the consequences may be more disastrous than you can imagine.

01:31:23.918 --> 01:31:27.218
You cannot foresee the results of even the most trivial act.

01:31:27.538 --> 01:31:32.098
You do not know the workings of all the forces that have been set moving in your behalf.

01:31:32.098 --> 01:31:35.178
Much may be depending on your doing some simple act.

01:31:35.418 --> 01:31:40.118
It may be the very thing which is to open the door of opportunity to very great possibilities.

01:31:40.678 --> 01:31:44.758
You can never know all the combinations which supreme intelligence is making for you in

01:31:44.758 --> 01:31:47.818
the world of things, and of things, and of human affairs.

01:31:48.398 --> 01:31:53.638
Your neglect or failure to do some small thing may cause a long delay in getting what you

01:31:53.638 --> 01:31:53.918
want.

01:31:54.738 --> 01:31:57.838
Do, every day, all that can be done that day.

01:31:57.838 --> 01:32:03.758
There is, however, a limitation or qualification of the above that you must take into account.

01:32:04.138 --> 01:32:08.918
You are not to overwork, nor to rush blindly into your business in the effort to do the

01:32:08.918 --> 01:32:12.318
greatest possible number of things in the shortest possible time.

01:32:12.778 --> 01:32:17.378
You are not to try to do tomorrow's work today, nor to do a week's work in a day.

01:32:17.938 --> 01:32:22.538
It is really not the number of things you do, but the efficiency of each separate action

01:32:22.538 --> 01:32:23.178
that counts.

01:32:23.738 --> 01:32:27.818
Every act is, in itself, either a success or a failure.

01:32:28.198 --> 01:32:32.018
Every act is, in itself, either effective or inefficient.

01:32:32.718 --> 01:32:37.938
Every inefficient act is a failure, and if you spend your life in doing inefficient acts,

01:32:38.298 --> 01:32:39.978
your whole life will be a failure.

01:32:40.678 --> 01:32:45.338
The more things you do, the worse is for you, if all your acts are inefficient ones.

01:32:45.938 --> 01:32:51.398
On the other hand, every efficient act is a success in itself, and if every act of your

01:32:51.398 --> 01:32:55.158
life is an efficient one, your whole life must be a success.

01:32:55.898 --> 01:33:00.978
The cause of failure is doing too many things in an inefficient manner, and not doing enough

01:33:00.978 --> 01:33:02.578
things in an efficient manner.

01:33:03.118 --> 01:33:08.738
You will see that it is a self-evident proposition that if you do not do any inefficient acts,

01:33:09.038 --> 01:33:13.578
and if you do a sufficient number of efficient acts, you will become rich.

01:33:13.998 --> 01:33:19.558
If now it is possible for you to make each act an efficient one, you see again that the

01:33:19.558 --> 01:33:23.578
getting of riches is reduced to an exact science, like mathematics.

01:33:24.518 --> 01:33:29.378
The matter turns then on the questions whether you can make each separate act a success in

01:33:29.378 --> 01:33:31.858
itself, and this you can certainly do.

01:33:32.338 --> 01:33:37.638
You can make each act a success, because all power is working with you, and all power cannot

01:33:37.638 --> 01:33:38.178
fail.

01:33:38.878 --> 01:33:43.858
Power is at your service, and to make each act efficient, you have only to put power

01:33:43.858 --> 01:33:44.538
into it.

01:33:45.058 --> 01:33:50.198
Every action is either strong or weak, and when everyone is strong, you are acting in

01:33:50.198 --> 01:33:52.278
a certain way which will make you rich.

01:33:53.018 --> 01:33:57.338
Every act can be made strong and efficient by holding your vision while you are doing

01:33:57.338 --> 01:34:00.798
it, and putting the whole power of your faith and purpose into it.

01:34:01.558 --> 01:34:06.378
It is at this point that people fail to separate mental power from personal action.

01:34:06.678 --> 01:34:11.438
They use the power of mind in one place and at one time, and they act in another place

01:34:11.438 --> 01:34:15.518
and at another time, so their acts are not successful in themselves.

01:34:16.018 --> 01:34:17.718
Too many of them are inefficient.

01:34:18.318 --> 01:34:23.838
But if all power goes into every act, no matter how commonplace, every act will be a success

01:34:23.838 --> 01:34:29.118
in itself, and as in the nature of things, every success opens the way to other successes,

01:34:29.538 --> 01:34:34.078
your progress toward what you want, and the progress of what you want toward you, will

01:34:34.078 --> 01:34:35.638
become increasingly rapid.

01:34:36.258 --> 01:34:39.538
Remember that successful action is cumulative in its results.

01:34:39.538 --> 01:34:45.138
Since the desire for more life is inherent in all things, when a man begins to move toward

01:34:45.138 --> 01:34:50.578
larger life, more things attach themselves to him, and the influence of his desire is

01:34:50.578 --> 01:34:51.198
multiplied.

01:34:52.118 --> 01:34:57.418
Do every day all that you can do that day, and do each act in an efficient manner.

01:34:58.078 --> 01:35:02.978
In saying that you must hold your vision while you are doing each act, however trivial or

01:35:02.978 --> 01:35:07.578
commonplace, I do not mean to say that it is necessary at all times to see the vision

01:35:07.578 --> 01:35:10.038
distinctly to all its smallest details.

01:35:10.658 --> 01:35:15.138
It should be the work of your leisure hours to use your imagination on the details of

01:35:15.138 --> 01:35:19.258
your vision, and to contemplate them until they are firmly fixed upon memory.

01:35:19.938 --> 01:35:24.578
If you wish speedier results, spend practically all your spare time in this practice.

01:35:25.318 --> 01:35:30.078
By continuous contemplation you will get the picture of what you want, even to the smallest

01:35:30.078 --> 01:35:35.718
details, so firmly fixed upon your mind, and so completely transferred to the mind of formless

01:35:35.718 --> 01:35:40.758
that in your working hours you need only to mentally refer to the picture to stimulate

01:35:40.758 --> 01:35:44.458
your faith and purpose, and cause your best effort to be put forth.

01:35:45.038 --> 01:35:49.938
Contemplate your picture in your leisure hours until your consciousness is so full of that,

01:35:50.138 --> 01:35:51.718
that you can grasp it instantly.

01:35:52.318 --> 01:35:57.098
You will become so enthused in its bright promises that the mere thought of it will

01:35:57.098 --> 01:36:00.218
call forth the strongest energies of your whole being.

01:36:00.598 --> 01:36:05.698
Let us again repeat our syllabus, and by slightly changing the closing statements, bring it

01:36:05.698 --> 01:36:07.538
to the point we have now reached.

01:36:08.098 --> 01:36:13.018
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which in its original state

01:36:13.018 --> 01:36:16.678
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

01:36:17.198 --> 01:36:21.418
A thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

01:36:22.138 --> 01:36:27.238
Man can form things in his thought, and by impressing his thought upon formless substance

01:36:27.238 --> 01:36:30.258
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

01:36:30.898 --> 01:36:35.358
In order to do this, man must pass from the competitive to the creative mind.

01:36:35.738 --> 01:36:40.758
He must form a clear mental picture of the things he wants, and do with faith and purpose

01:36:40.758 --> 01:36:45.978
all that can be done each day, doing each separate thing in an efficient manner.

01:37:08.043 --> 01:37:13.313
Success in any particular business depends for one thing upon your possessing in a well-developed

01:37:13.313 --> 01:37:19.393
state the faculties required in that business. Without good musical faculty no one can succeed

01:37:19.393 --> 01:37:24.693
as a teacher of music. Without well-developed mechanical faculties no one can achieve great

01:37:24.693 --> 01:37:30.053
success in any of the mechanical trades. Without tech and the commercial faculties no one

01:37:30.053 --> 01:37:35.473
can succeed in mercantile pursuits. But to possess in a well-developed state the faculties

01:37:35.473 --> 01:37:40.493
required in your particular vocation does not ensure getting rich. There are musicians

01:37:40.493 --> 01:37:46.253
who have remarkable talent and who yet remain poor. There are blacksmiths, carpenters and

01:37:46.253 --> 01:37:51.673
so on who have excellent mechanical ability but who do not get rich. And there are merchants

01:37:51.673 --> 01:37:57.173
with good faculties for dealing with men who nevertheless fail. The different faculties

01:37:57.173 --> 01:38:02.653
are tools. It is essential to have good tools but it is also essential that the tools should

01:38:02.653 --> 01:38:09.053
be used in the right way. One man can take a sharp saw, a square, a good plane and so

01:38:09.053 --> 01:38:14.473
on and build a handsome article of furniture. Another man can take the same tools and set

01:38:14.473 --> 01:38:20.893
to work to duplicate the article but his production will be a botch. He does not know how to use

01:38:20.893 --> 01:38:26.513
good tools in a successful way. The various faculties of your mind are the tools with

01:38:26.513 --> 01:38:31.373
which you must do the work which is to make you rich. It will be easier for you to succeed

01:38:31.373 --> 01:38:36.393
if you get into a business for which you are well equipped with mental tools. Generally

01:38:36.393 --> 01:38:41.753
speaking you will do best in that business which will use your strongest faculties, the

01:38:41.753 --> 01:38:46.353
one for which you are naturally best fitted. But there are limitations to this statement

01:38:46.353 --> 01:38:51.893
also. No man should regard his vocation as being irrevocably fixed by the tendencies

01:38:51.893 --> 01:38:56.913
with which he was born. You can get rich in any business for if you have not the right

01:38:56.913 --> 01:39:02.233
talent you can develop that talent. It merely means that you will have to make your tools

01:39:02.233 --> 01:39:07.353
as you go along instead of confining yourself to the use of those with which you were born.

01:39:07.353 --> 01:39:12.353
It will be easier for you to succeed in a vocation for which you already have the talents

01:39:12.353 --> 01:39:18.393
in a well developed state. But you can succeed in any vocation for you can develop any rudimentary

01:39:18.393 --> 01:39:23.733
talent and there is no talent of which you have not at least the rudiment. You will get

01:39:23.733 --> 01:39:28.633
rich most easily in point of effort if you do that for which you are best fitted but

01:39:28.633 --> 01:39:34.393
you will get rich most satisfactorily if you do that which you want to do. Doing what you

01:39:34.393 --> 01:39:39.853
want to do is life and there is no real satisfaction in living if we are compelled to be forever

01:39:39.853 --> 01:39:45.073
doing something which we do not like to do and can never do what we want to do. And it

01:39:45.073 --> 01:39:49.913
is certain that you can do what you want to do. The desire to do it is proof that you

01:39:49.913 --> 01:39:55.873
have within you the power which can do it. Desire is a manifestation of power. The desire

01:39:55.873 --> 01:40:00.093
to play music is the power which can play music seeking expression and development.

01:40:00.493 --> 01:40:05.453
The desire to invent mechanical devices is the mechanical talent seeking expression and

01:40:05.453 --> 01:40:10.653
development. Where there is no power either developed or undeveloped to do a thing there

01:40:10.653 --> 01:40:15.493
is never any desire to do that thing. And where there is strong desire to do a thing

01:40:15.493 --> 01:40:20.653
it is certain proof that the power to do it is strong and only requires to be developed

01:40:20.653 --> 01:40:26.813
and applied in the right way. All things else being equal it is best to select a business

01:40:26.813 --> 01:40:31.273
for which you have the best developed talent but if you have a strong desire to engage

01:40:31.273 --> 01:40:36.133
in any particular line of work you should select that work as the ultimate end at which

01:40:36.133 --> 01:40:41.453
you aim. You can do what you want to do and it is your right and privilege to follow the

01:40:41.453 --> 01:40:47.633
business or avocation which will be most congenial and pleasant. You are not obliged to do what

01:40:47.633 --> 01:40:52.433
you do not like to do and you should not do it except as the means to bring you to the

01:40:52.433 --> 01:40:58.253
of the thing you want to do. If there are past mistakes whose consequences have placed you in

01:40:58.253 --> 01:41:03.373
an undesirable business or environment you may be obliged for some time to do what you do not like

01:41:03.373 --> 01:41:08.573
to do but you can make the doing of it pleasant by knowing that it is making it possible for you

01:41:08.573 --> 01:41:13.693
to come to the doing of what you want to do. If you feel that you are not in the right vocation

01:41:13.693 --> 01:41:18.833
do not act too hastily in trying to get into another one. The best way generally to change

01:41:18.833 --> 01:41:24.013
business or environment is by growth. Do not be afraid to make a sudden and radical change

01:41:24.013 --> 01:41:29.273
if the opportunity is presented and you feel after careful consideration that it is the right

01:41:29.273 --> 01:41:34.993
opportunity but never take sudden or radical action when you are in doubt as to the wisdom

01:41:34.993 --> 01:41:40.913
of doing so. There is never any hurry on the creative plane and there is no lack of opportunity.

01:41:41.673 --> 01:41:46.873
When you get out of the competitive mind you will understand that you never need to act hastily.

01:41:46.873 --> 01:41:52.573
No one else is going to beat you to the thing you want to do. There is enough for all. If one

01:41:52.573 --> 01:41:57.673
space is taken another and a better one will be opened for you a little further on. There is

01:41:57.673 --> 01:42:03.513
plenty of time. When you are in doubt, wait. Fall back on the contemplation of your vision

01:42:03.513 --> 01:42:08.953
and increase your faith and purpose and by all means in times of doubt and indecision

01:42:08.953 --> 01:42:14.433
cultivate gratitude. A day or two spent in contemplating the vision of what you want

01:42:14.433 --> 01:42:20.313
and in earnest thanksgiving that you are getting it will bring your mind into such close relationship

01:42:20.313 --> 01:42:26.133
with the Supreme that you will make no mistake when you do act. There is a mind which knows all

01:42:26.133 --> 01:42:31.093
there is to know and you can come into close unity with this mind by faith and the purpose

01:42:31.093 --> 01:42:37.553
to advance in life if you have deep gratitude. Mistakes come from acting hastily or from acting

01:42:37.553 --> 01:42:43.693
in fear or doubt or in forgetfulness of the right motive which is more life to all and less to none.

01:42:44.253 --> 01:42:49.013
As you go on in the certain way opportunities will come to you in increasing number

01:42:49.013 --> 01:42:54.353
and you will need to be very steady in your faith and purpose and to keep in close touch with the

01:42:54.353 --> 01:43:00.553
old mind by reverent gratitude. Do all that you can do in a perfect manner every day but do it

01:43:00.553 --> 01:43:07.333
without haste, worry or fear. Go as fast as you can but never hurry. Remember that in the moment

01:43:07.333 --> 01:43:13.093
you begin to hurry you cease to be a creator and become a competitor you drop back upon the old

01:43:13.093 --> 01:43:19.533
plane again. Whenever you find yourself hurrying call a halt. Fix your attention on the mental

01:43:19.533 --> 01:43:24.833
image of the thing you want and begin to give thanks that you are getting it. The exercise

01:43:24.833 --> 01:43:32.353
of gratitude will never fail to strengthen your faith and renew your purpose.

01:43:49.212 --> 01:43:51.192
THE IMPRESSION OF INCREASE.

01:43:52.072 --> 01:43:56.672
Whether you charge your vocation or not, your actions for the present must be those pertaining

01:43:56.672 --> 01:43:58.812
to the business in which you are now engaged.

01:43:59.212 --> 01:44:03.772
You can get into the business you want by making constructive use of the business you

01:44:03.772 --> 01:44:07.732
are already established in, by doing your daily work in a certain way.

01:44:08.512 --> 01:44:13.152
And in so far as your business consists in dealing with other men, whether personally

01:44:13.152 --> 01:44:18.012
or by letter, the key thought of all your efforts must be to convey their minds the

01:44:18.012 --> 01:44:19.112
impression of increase.

01:44:20.012 --> 01:44:22.792
Increase is what all men and all women are seeking.

01:44:23.212 --> 01:44:27.412
It is the urge of the formless intelligence within them, seeking fuller expression.

01:44:27.992 --> 01:44:30.852
The desire for increase is inherent in all nature.

01:44:30.852 --> 01:44:33.752
It is the fundamental impulse of the universe.

01:44:34.452 --> 01:44:37.632
All human activities are based on the desire for increase.

01:44:38.132 --> 01:44:43.432
People are seeking more food, more clothes, better shelter, more luxury, more beauty,

01:44:43.572 --> 01:44:45.132
more knowledge, more pleasure.

01:44:45.612 --> 01:44:47.512
Increase in something, more life.

01:44:48.252 --> 01:44:53.212
Every living thing is under this necessity for continuous advancement, where increase

01:44:53.212 --> 01:44:56.852
of life ceases, dissolution and death set in at once.

01:44:57.572 --> 01:45:01.632
Man instinctively knows this, and hence he is forever seeking more.

01:45:02.072 --> 01:45:07.032
This law of perpetual increase is set forth by Jesus in the parable of the talents.

01:45:07.552 --> 01:45:09.852
Only those who gain more retain any.

01:45:10.152 --> 01:45:14.032
From him who had not shall be taken away even that which he had.

01:45:14.932 --> 01:45:19.572
The normal desire for increased wealth is not an evil or a reprehensible thing.

01:45:19.952 --> 01:45:22.432
It is simply the desire for more abundant life.

01:45:22.572 --> 01:45:23.632
It is aspiration.

01:45:23.632 --> 01:45:29.452
And because it is the deepest instinct of their natures, all men and women are attracted

01:45:29.452 --> 01:45:32.172
to him, who can give them more of the means of life.

01:45:32.952 --> 01:45:37.732
In following the certain way as described in the foregoing pages, you are getting continuous

01:45:37.732 --> 01:45:41.632
increase for yourself, and you are giving it to all with whom you deal.

01:45:42.472 --> 01:45:46.492
You are a creative center, from which increase is given off to all.

01:45:47.232 --> 01:45:52.652
Be sure of this, and convey assurance of the fact to every man, woman and child with whom

01:45:52.652 --> 01:45:53.732
you come in contact.

01:45:54.412 --> 01:45:59.352
No matter how small the transaction, even if it be only the selling of a stick of candy

01:45:59.352 --> 01:46:04.272
to a little child, put into it the thought of increase, and make sure that the customer

01:46:04.272 --> 01:46:05.792
is impressed with the thought.

01:46:06.792 --> 01:46:11.032
Convey the impression of advancement with everything you do, so that all people shall

01:46:11.032 --> 01:46:15.672
receive the impression that you are an advancing man, and that you advance all who deal with

01:46:15.672 --> 01:46:16.052
you.

01:46:16.712 --> 01:46:21.472
Even to the people whom you met in a social way, without any thought of business, and

01:46:21.472 --> 01:46:25.172
to whom you do not try to sell anything, give the thought of increase.

01:46:25.912 --> 01:46:30.812
You can convey this impression by holding the unshakable faith that you, yourself, are

01:46:30.812 --> 01:46:36.192
in the way of increase, and by letting this faith aspire, fill and permeate every action.

01:46:36.892 --> 01:46:41.712
Do everything that you do in a firm conviction that you are an advancing personality, and

01:46:41.712 --> 01:46:43.652
that you are giving advancement to everybody.

01:46:44.412 --> 01:46:49.672
Feel that you are getting rich, and that in doing so you are making others rich, and conferring

01:46:49.672 --> 01:46:50.772
benefits on all.

01:46:51.472 --> 01:46:55.732
Do not boast or brag of your success, or talk about it unnecessarily.

01:46:56.172 --> 01:46:57.972
True faith is never boastful.

01:46:59.052 --> 01:47:04.152
Wherever you find a boastful person, you find one who is secretly doubtful and afraid.

01:47:04.592 --> 01:47:08.392
Simply feel the faith, and let it work out in every transaction.

01:47:08.752 --> 01:47:13.332
Let every act and tone and look express the quiet assurance that you are getting rich,

01:47:13.652 --> 01:47:14.992
that you are already rich.

01:47:15.632 --> 01:47:18.732
Words will not be necessary to communicate this feeling to others.

01:47:19.112 --> 01:47:23.372
They will feel the sense of increase when in your presence, and will be attracted to

01:47:23.372 --> 01:47:24.012
you again.

01:47:24.772 --> 01:47:29.132
You must so impress others that they will feel that in associating with you they will

01:47:29.132 --> 01:47:33.872
get increase for themselves, see that you give them a use of value greater than the

01:47:33.872 --> 01:47:35.792
cash value you are taking from them.

01:47:36.712 --> 01:47:41.272
Take an honest pride in doing this, and let everybody know it, and you will have no lack

01:47:41.272 --> 01:47:42.072
of customers.

01:47:42.792 --> 01:47:47.552
People will go where they are given increase, and the supreme which desires increase in

01:47:47.552 --> 01:47:52.432
and which knows all, will move toward you men and women who have never heard of you.

01:47:52.952 --> 01:47:57.772
Your business will increase rapidly, and you will be surprised at the unexpected benefits

01:47:57.772 --> 01:47:58.932
which will come to you.

01:47:59.432 --> 01:48:05.072
You will be able from day to day to make larger combinations, secure greater advantages, and

01:48:05.072 --> 01:48:09.192
to go on into a more congenial vocation if you desire to do so.

01:48:09.772 --> 01:48:14.392
But in doing all this, you must never lose sight of your vision of what you want, or

01:48:14.392 --> 01:48:16.652
your faith and purpose to get what you want.

01:48:17.132 --> 01:48:20.552
Let me here give you another word of caution in regard to motives.

01:48:21.372 --> 01:48:25.272
Beware of the insidious temptation to seek for power over other men.

01:48:25.652 --> 01:48:30.452
Nothing is so pleasant to the unformed or partially developed mind as the exercise of

01:48:30.452 --> 01:48:32.452
power or domination over others.

01:48:32.992 --> 01:48:37.352
The desire to rule for selfish gratification has been the curse of the world.

01:48:37.792 --> 01:48:42.312
For countless ages kings and lords have drenched the earth with blood in their battles to

01:48:42.312 --> 01:48:43.652
extend their dominions.

01:48:44.232 --> 01:48:48.032
This not to seek more life for all, but to get more power for themselves.

01:48:48.592 --> 01:48:52.572
Today the main motive in the business and industrial world is the same.

01:48:52.972 --> 01:48:57.812
Men marshal their armies of dollars, and they waste the lives and hearts of millions in

01:48:57.812 --> 01:49:00.252
the same mad scramble for power over others.

01:49:00.772 --> 01:49:05.612
Commercial kings, like political kings, are inspired by the lust for power.

01:49:06.512 --> 01:49:11.972
Jesus saw in this desire for mastery the moving impulse of that evil world he sought to overthrow.

01:49:12.552 --> 01:49:18.112
Read the 23rd chapter of Matthew and see how he pictures the lust of the Pharisees to be

01:49:18.112 --> 01:49:23.412
called master, to sit in the high places, to domineer over others, and to lay burdens

01:49:23.412 --> 01:49:25.052
on the backs of the less fortunate.

01:49:25.512 --> 01:49:30.052
And note how he compares this lust for domination with the brotherly seeking for the common

01:49:30.052 --> 01:49:32.172
good to which he calls his disciples.

01:49:32.832 --> 01:49:38.472
Look out for the temptation to seek for authority, to become a master, to be considered as one

01:49:38.472 --> 01:49:43.112
who is above the common herd, to impress others by lavish display, and so on.

01:49:43.412 --> 01:49:48.232
The mind that seeks for mastery over others is the competitive mind, and the competitive

01:49:48.232 --> 01:49:50.152
mind is not the creative one.

01:49:50.612 --> 01:49:55.432
In order to master your environment and your destiny, it is not at all necessary that you

01:49:55.432 --> 01:49:59.672
should rule over your fellow man, and indeed, when you fall into the world's struggle for

01:49:59.672 --> 01:50:04.592
the high places, you begin to be conquered by fate and environment, and your getting

01:50:04.592 --> 01:50:07.112
rich becomes a matter of chance and speculation.

01:50:07.732 --> 01:50:09.672
Beware of the competitive mind.

01:50:10.032 --> 01:50:14.752
No better statement of the principle of creative action can be formulated than the favorite

01:50:14.752 --> 01:50:17.912
declaration of the late Golden Rule Jones of Toledo.

01:50:18.612 --> 01:50:21.512
What I want for myself, I want for everybody.

01:50:40.227 --> 01:50:41.547
THE ADVANCING MAN

01:50:42.247 --> 01:50:46.947
What I have said in the last chapter applies as well to the professional man and the wage-earner

01:50:46.947 --> 01:50:50.167
as to the man who is engaged in mercantile business.

01:50:51.147 --> 01:50:56.227
No matter whether you are a physician, a teacher, or a clergyman, if you can give increase of

01:50:56.227 --> 01:51:01.647
and make them sensible of the fact, they will be attracted to you, and you will get rich.

01:51:02.287 --> 01:51:07.147
The physician who holds the vision of himself as a great and successful healer, and who

01:51:07.147 --> 01:51:11.487
works toward the complete realization of that vision with faith and purpose, as described

01:51:11.487 --> 01:51:15.987
in the former chapters, will come into such close touch with the source of life that he

01:51:15.987 --> 01:51:17.767
will be phenomenally successful.

01:51:18.287 --> 01:51:20.187
Patience will come to him in throngs.

01:51:20.907 --> 01:51:25.327
No one has a greater opportunity to carry into effect the teaching of this book than

01:51:25.327 --> 01:51:27.007
the practitioner of medicine.

01:51:27.547 --> 01:51:32.067
It does not matter to which of the various schools he may belong, for the principle of

01:51:32.067 --> 01:51:35.547
healing is common to all of them, and may be reached by all alike.

01:51:36.167 --> 01:51:41.047
The advancing man in medicine, who holds to a clear mental image of himself as successful,

01:51:41.367 --> 01:51:46.507
and who obeys the laws of faith, purpose, and gratitude, will cure every curable case

01:51:46.507 --> 01:51:49.687
he undertakes, no matter what remedies he may use.

01:51:50.307 --> 01:51:55.047
In the field of religion, the word cries out for the clergyman who can teach his hearers

01:51:55.047 --> 01:51:56.907
the true science of abundant life.

01:51:57.447 --> 01:52:02.227
He who masters the details of the science of getting rich, together with allied sciences

01:52:02.227 --> 01:52:07.487
of being well, of being great, and of winning love, and who teaches these details from the

01:52:07.487 --> 01:52:10.047
pulpit, will never lack for a congregation.

01:52:10.667 --> 01:52:12.787
This is the gospel that the world needs.

01:52:13.147 --> 01:52:18.087
It will give increase of life, and men will hear it gladly, and will give liberal support

01:52:18.087 --> 01:52:19.707
to the man who brings it to them.

01:52:20.307 --> 01:52:24.307
What is now needed is the demonstration of science of life from the pulpit.

01:52:24.307 --> 01:52:29.627
We want preachers who can not only tell us how, but who in their own persons will show

01:52:29.627 --> 01:52:30.287
us how.

01:52:30.747 --> 01:52:35.987
We need the preacher, who will himself be rich, healthy, great, and beloved, to teach

01:52:35.987 --> 01:52:41.067
us how to attain these things, and when he comes, he will find a numerous and loyal following.

01:52:41.687 --> 01:52:45.987
The same is true for the teacher, who can inspire the children with the faith and purpose

01:52:45.987 --> 01:52:47.147
of the advancing life.

01:52:47.427 --> 01:52:49.287
He will never be out of a job.

01:52:49.727 --> 01:52:53.547
And any teacher who has this faith and purpose can give it to his pupils.

01:52:53.547 --> 01:52:58.307
He cannot help giving it to them, if it is a part of his own life and practice.

01:52:59.127 --> 01:53:03.627
What is true of the teacher, preacher, and physician, is true of the lawyer, dentist,

01:53:03.847 --> 01:53:06.687
real estate man, insurance agent, of everybody.

01:53:07.267 --> 01:53:11.247
The combined mental and personal action I have described is infallible.

01:53:11.507 --> 01:53:12.487
It cannot fail.

01:53:13.107 --> 01:53:17.987
Every man and woman who follows these instructions steadily, perseveringly, and to the latter,

01:53:18.167 --> 01:53:18.947
will get rich.

01:53:19.367 --> 01:53:25.467
The law of the increase of life is as mathematically certain in its operation as the law of gravitation.

01:53:26.287 --> 01:53:28.347
Getting rich is an exact science.

01:53:29.187 --> 01:53:33.787
The wage earner will find this as true of his case as of any of the others mentioned.

01:53:34.307 --> 01:53:38.267
Do not feel that you have no chance to get rich because you are working where there is

01:53:38.267 --> 01:53:43.467
no visible opportunity for advancement, where wages are small and the cost of living high.

01:53:43.467 --> 01:53:48.707
Form your clear mental vision of what you want and begin to act with faith and purpose.

01:53:49.487 --> 01:53:54.467
Do all the work you can do, every day, and do each piece of work in a perfectly successful

01:53:54.467 --> 01:53:54.927
manner.

01:53:55.347 --> 01:53:59.827
Put the power of success and the purpose to get rich into everything that you do.

01:54:00.427 --> 01:54:05.287
But do not do this merely with the idea of carrying favor with your employer in the hope

01:54:05.287 --> 01:54:09.227
that he, or those above you, will see your good work and advance you.

01:54:09.427 --> 01:54:11.487
It is not likely that they will do so.

01:54:12.107 --> 01:54:16.707
The man who is merely a good workman, filling his place to the very best of his ability,

01:54:17.007 --> 01:54:20.007
and satisfied with that, is valuable to his employer.

01:54:20.387 --> 01:54:23.247
And it is not to the employer's interest to promote him.

01:54:23.407 --> 01:54:25.127
He is worth more where he is.

01:54:25.767 --> 01:54:30.347
To secure advancement, something more is necessary than to be too large for your place.

01:54:31.007 --> 01:54:35.567
The man who is certain to advance is the one who is too big for his place, and who has

01:54:35.567 --> 01:54:40.207
a clear concept of what he wants to be, who knows that he can become what he wants to

01:54:40.207 --> 01:54:42.807
be, and who is determined to be what he wants to be.

01:54:43.227 --> 01:54:47.207
Do not try to more than fill your present place with the view of pleasing your employer.

01:54:47.667 --> 01:54:49.907
Do it with the idea of advancing yourself.

01:54:50.367 --> 01:54:55.447
Hold the faith and purpose of increase during work hours, after work hours, and before work

01:54:55.447 --> 01:54:55.827
hours.

01:54:56.627 --> 01:55:01.027
Hold it in such a way that every person who comes in contact with you, whether foremen,

01:55:01.307 --> 01:55:06.247
fellow workmen, or social acquaintance, will feel the power of purpose radiating from you,

01:55:06.247 --> 01:55:10.007
so that everyone will get the sense of advancement and increase from you.

01:55:10.527 --> 01:55:14.747
Man will be attracted to you, and if there is no possibility for advancement in your

01:55:14.747 --> 01:55:18.687
present job, you will very soon see an opportunity to take another job.

01:55:19.107 --> 01:55:24.327
There is a power which never fails to present opportunity to the advancing man who is moving

01:55:24.327 --> 01:55:25.567
in obedience to law.

01:55:26.127 --> 01:55:29.367
God cannot help helping you if you act in a certain way.

01:55:29.687 --> 01:55:32.047
He must do so in order to help himself.

01:55:32.047 --> 01:55:37.047
There is nothing in your circumstances or the industrial situation that can keep you

01:55:37.047 --> 01:55:37.387
down.

01:55:37.987 --> 01:55:42.867
If you cannot get rich working for the steel trust, you can get rich on a ten-acre farm,

01:55:43.187 --> 01:55:47.207
and if you begin to move in a certain way, you will certainly escape from the clutches

01:55:47.207 --> 01:55:51.447
of the steel trust and get on to the farm or wherever else you wish to be.

01:55:52.027 --> 01:55:56.767
If a few thousands of its employees would enter upon a certain way, the steel trust

01:55:56.767 --> 01:55:58.247
would soon be in a bad plight.

01:55:58.247 --> 01:56:02.887
It would have to give its working man more opportunity or to go out of business.

01:56:03.647 --> 01:56:05.327
Nobody has to work for a trust.

01:56:05.647 --> 01:56:11.067
The trusts can keep man in so-called hopeless conditions only so long as there are men who

01:56:11.067 --> 01:56:15.767
are too ignorant to know of the science of getting rich or too intellectually slothful

01:56:15.767 --> 01:56:16.867
to practice it.

01:56:17.567 --> 01:56:21.847
Begin this way of thinking and acting, and your faith and purpose will make you quick

01:56:21.847 --> 01:56:24.407
to see any opportunity to better your condition.

01:56:24.867 --> 01:56:29.847
Such opportunities will speedily come, for the Supreme, working in all, and working for

01:56:29.847 --> 01:56:31.827
you, will bring them before you.

01:56:32.607 --> 01:56:35.707
Do not wait for an opportunity to be all that you want to be.

01:56:36.047 --> 01:56:40.687
When an opportunity to be more than you are now is presented, and you feel impelled toward

01:56:40.687 --> 01:56:41.727
it, take it.

01:56:42.147 --> 01:56:44.867
It will be the first step toward a greater opportunity.

01:56:45.567 --> 01:56:50.347
There is no such thing possible in this universe as the lack of opportunities for the man who

01:56:50.347 --> 01:56:51.867
is living the advancing life.

01:56:51.867 --> 01:56:56.987
It is inherent in the Constitution of the Cosmos that all things shall be for him and

01:56:56.987 --> 01:57:02.287
work together for his good, and he must certainly get rich if he acts and thinks in the certain

01:57:02.287 --> 01:57:02.707
way.

01:57:03.267 --> 01:57:08.467
So let wage-earning men and women study this book with great care, and enter with confidence

01:57:08.467 --> 01:57:10.467
upon the course of action it prescribes.

01:57:10.727 --> 01:57:11.967
It will not fail.

01:57:30.971 --> 01:57:34.391
SOME CAUTIONS AND CONCLUDING OBSERVATIONS.

01:57:34.631 --> 01:57:38.691
Many people will scoff at the idea that there is an exact science of getting rich.

01:57:39.111 --> 01:57:43.831
Holding the impression that the supply of wealth is limited, they will insist that social

01:57:43.831 --> 01:57:48.831
and governmental constitutions must be changed before even any considerable number of people

01:57:48.831 --> 01:57:50.231
can acquire a competence.

01:57:50.791 --> 01:57:51.971
But this is not true.

01:57:52.451 --> 01:57:57.331
It is true that existing governments keep the masses in poverty, but this is because

01:57:57.331 --> 01:58:00.171
the masses do not think and act in a certain way.

01:58:00.831 --> 01:58:06.251
If the masses begin to move forward as suggested in this book, neither governments nor industrial

01:58:06.251 --> 01:58:07.671
systems can check them.

01:58:07.971 --> 01:58:11.551
All systems must be modified to accommodate the forward movement.

01:58:12.271 --> 01:58:17.251
If the people have the advancing mind, have the faith that they can become rich and move

01:58:17.251 --> 01:58:21.851
the fixed purpose to become rich, nothing can possibly keep them in poverty.

01:58:22.891 --> 01:58:27.771
Individuals may enter upon the certain way at any time and under any government and make

01:58:27.771 --> 01:58:32.791
themselves rich, and when any considerable number of individuals do so under any government,

01:58:33.111 --> 01:58:37.011
they will cause the system to be so modified as to open the way for others.

01:58:37.711 --> 01:58:42.451
The more men who get rich on the competitive plane, the worse for others, and more who

01:58:42.451 --> 01:58:45.591
get rich in the creative plane, the better for others.

01:58:46.211 --> 01:58:50.731
The economic salvation of the masses can only be accomplished by getting a large number

01:58:50.731 --> 01:58:55.131
of people to practice the scientific method set down in this book and become rich.

01:58:55.631 --> 01:59:01.011
These will show others the way, and inspire them with a desire for real life, with a faith

01:59:01.011 --> 01:59:03.971
that can be attained, and with the purpose to attain it.

01:59:04.671 --> 01:59:08.611
For the present, however, it is enough to know that neither the government under which

01:59:08.611 --> 01:59:13.271
you live nor the capitalistic or competitive system of industry can keep you from getting

01:59:13.271 --> 01:59:13.691
rich.

01:59:14.111 --> 01:59:18.751
When you enter upon the creative plane of thought, you will rise above all these things

01:59:18.751 --> 01:59:20.911
and become a citizen of another kingdom.

01:59:21.731 --> 01:59:25.071
But remember that your thought must be held upon the creative plane.

01:59:25.471 --> 01:59:30.251
You are never for an instant to be betrayed into regarding the supply as limited, or into

01:59:30.251 --> 01:59:32.391
acting on the moral level of competition.

01:59:33.491 --> 01:59:37.571
Whenever you do fall into old ways of thought, correct yourself instantly.

01:59:38.191 --> 01:59:42.291
For when you are in the competitive mind, you have lost the cooperation of the mind

01:59:42.291 --> 01:59:42.951
of the whole.

01:59:43.711 --> 01:59:47.951
Do not spend any time in planning as to how you will meet possible emergencies in the

01:59:47.951 --> 01:59:51.951
future, except as the necessary policies may affect your actions today.

01:59:52.531 --> 01:59:56.791
You are concerned with doing today's work in a perfectly successful manner, and not

01:59:56.791 --> 01:59:58.851
with emergencies which may arise tomorrow.

01:59:59.031 --> 02:00:00.851
You can attend to them as they come.

02:00:01.371 --> 02:00:05.931
Do not concern yourself with questions as to how you shall surmount obstacles which

02:00:05.931 --> 02:00:10.851
may loom upon your business horizon, unless you see plainly that your course must be altered

02:00:10.851 --> 02:00:12.471
in order to avoid them.

02:00:12.851 --> 02:00:17.211
No matter how tremendous an obstruction may appear at the distance, you will find that

02:00:17.211 --> 02:00:22.511
if you go in a certain way, it will disappear as you approach it, or that a way over, through,

02:00:22.651 --> 02:00:24.071
or around it will appear.

02:00:24.851 --> 02:00:29.751
No possible combination of circumstances can defeat a man or woman who is proceeding to

02:00:29.751 --> 02:00:32.251
get rich along strictly scientific lines.

02:00:32.831 --> 02:00:38.291
No man or woman who obeys the law can fail to get rich, any more than one can multiply

02:00:38.291 --> 02:00:40.571
two by two, and fail to get four.

02:00:41.251 --> 02:00:46.551
Give no anxious thought to possible disasters, obstacles, panics, or unfavourable combinations

02:00:46.551 --> 02:00:47.531
of circumstances.

02:00:48.111 --> 02:00:52.371
It is time enough to meet such things as they present themselves before you in the immediate

02:00:52.371 --> 02:00:57.651
present, and you will find that every difficulty carries with it the wherewithal for its overcoming.

02:00:58.231 --> 02:00:59.171
Guard your speech.

02:00:59.531 --> 02:01:04.671
Never speak of yourself, your affairs, or of anything else in a discouraged or discouraging

02:01:04.671 --> 02:01:05.091
way.

02:01:05.811 --> 02:01:11.351
Never admit the possibility of failure, or speak in a way that infers failure as a possibility.

02:01:12.331 --> 02:01:16.891
Never speak of the times as being hard, or of business conditions as being doubtful.

02:01:17.271 --> 02:01:21.891
Times may be hard and business doubtful for those who are on the competitive plane, but

02:01:21.891 --> 02:01:23.531
they can never be so for you.

02:01:23.911 --> 02:01:26.831
You can create what you want, and you are above fear.

02:01:27.591 --> 02:01:32.691
When others are having hard times and poor business, you will find your greatest opportunities.

02:01:33.451 --> 02:01:38.091
Train yourself to think of and to look upon the world as something which is becoming,

02:01:38.331 --> 02:01:43.151
which is growing, and to regard something evil as being only that which is undeveloped.

02:01:43.351 --> 02:01:45.271
Always speak in terms of advancement.

02:01:45.651 --> 02:01:50.491
To do otherwise is to deny your faith, and to deny your faith is to lose it.

02:01:51.291 --> 02:01:53.491
Never allow yourself to feel disappointed.

02:01:54.011 --> 02:01:58.851
You may expect to have a certain thing at a certain time, and not get it at that time,

02:01:59.231 --> 02:02:01.291
and this will appear to you like failure.

02:02:01.291 --> 02:02:06.131
But if you hold to your faith, you will find that the failure is only apparent.

02:02:06.791 --> 02:02:11.451
Go on in the certain way, and if you do not receive that thing, you will receive something

02:02:11.451 --> 02:02:16.111
so much better that you will see that the seeming failure was really a great success.

02:02:16.531 --> 02:02:21.431
A student in this science had set his mind on making a certain business combination which

02:02:21.431 --> 02:02:26.351
seemed to him at the time to be very desirable, and he worked for some weeks to bring it about.

02:02:26.891 --> 02:02:31.751
When the crucial time came, the thing failed in a perfectly inexplicable way.

02:02:32.031 --> 02:02:36.231
It was as if some unseen influence had been working secretly against him.

02:02:36.551 --> 02:02:42.331
He was not disappointed, on the contrary, he thanked God that his desire had been overruled,

02:02:42.511 --> 02:02:44.851
and went steadily on with a grateful mind.

02:02:45.311 --> 02:02:50.451
In a few weeks an opportunity so much better came his way that he would not have made the

02:02:50.451 --> 02:02:55.611
first deal on any account, and he saw that a mind which knew more than he knew had prevented

02:02:55.611 --> 02:02:59.611
him from losing the greater good by entangling himself with the lesser.

02:03:00.291 --> 02:03:05.391
That is the way every seeming failure will work out for you if you keep your faith, hold

02:03:05.391 --> 02:03:10.851
to your purpose, have gratitude, and do, every day, all that can be done that day, doing

02:03:10.851 --> 02:03:13.091
each separate act in a successful manner.

02:03:13.931 --> 02:03:17.331
When you make a failure, it is because you have not asked for enough.

02:03:17.791 --> 02:03:21.931
Keep on, and a larger thing than you were asking will certainly come to you.

02:03:22.211 --> 02:03:23.091
Remember this.

02:03:23.091 --> 02:03:27.451
You will not fail because you lack the necessary talent to do what you wish to do.

02:03:27.751 --> 02:03:32.311
If you go on as I have directed, you will develop all that talent that is necessary

02:03:32.311 --> 02:03:33.711
for the doing of your work.

02:03:34.471 --> 02:03:38.511
It is not within the scope of this book to deal with the science of cultivating talent,

02:03:38.651 --> 02:03:42.031
but it is as certain and simple as the process of getting rich.

02:03:42.951 --> 02:03:45.511
However, do not hesitate or waver for fear.

02:03:45.771 --> 02:03:49.191
When you come to any certain place you will fail for lack of ability.

02:03:49.591 --> 02:03:54.131
Keep right on, and when you come to that place the ability will be furnished for you.

02:03:54.451 --> 02:03:58.791
The same source of ability, which enabled the untaught Lincoln to do the greatest working

02:03:58.791 --> 02:04:02.031
government ever accomplished by a single man, is open to you.

02:04:02.351 --> 02:04:06.911
You may draw upon all the mind there is for wisdom to use in meeting the responsibilities

02:04:06.911 --> 02:04:08.411
which are laid upon you.

02:04:08.811 --> 02:04:10.271
Go on in full faith.

02:04:11.171 --> 02:04:12.031
Study this book.

02:04:12.431 --> 02:04:16.931
Make it your constant companion until you have mastered all the ideas contained in it.

02:04:16.931 --> 02:04:21.591
While you are getting firmly established in this faith, you will do well to give up most

02:04:21.591 --> 02:04:26.891
recreations and pleasure, and to stay away from places where ideas conflicting with these

02:04:26.891 --> 02:04:29.371
are advanced in lectures or sermons.

02:04:29.751 --> 02:04:34.831
Do not read pessimistic or conflicting literature, or get into arguments upon the matter.

02:04:35.551 --> 02:04:39.471
Do very little reading, outside of the writers mentioned in the preface.

02:04:40.011 --> 02:04:44.751
Spend most of your leisure time in contemplating your vision, and in cultivating gratitude,

02:04:45.091 --> 02:04:46.211
and in reading this book.

02:04:46.651 --> 02:04:51.431
It contains all you need to know of the science of getting rich, and you will find all the

02:04:51.431 --> 02:04:53.791
essentials summed up in the following chapter.

02:05:13.236 --> 02:05:15.036
SUMMARY OF THE SCIENCE OF GETTING RICH

02:05:15.876 --> 02:05:21.196
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

02:05:21.476 --> 02:05:24.936
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

02:05:25.676 --> 02:05:29.796
A thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

02:05:29.796 --> 02:05:35.576
Man can form things in his thought, and by impressing his thought upon formless substance

02:05:35.576 --> 02:05:38.616
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

02:05:39.136 --> 02:05:44.196
In order to do this, man must pass from the competitive to the creative mind, otherwise

02:05:44.196 --> 02:05:48.536
he cannot be in harmony with the formless intelligence, which is always creative and

02:05:48.536 --> 02:05:50.256
never competitive in spirit.

02:05:50.976 --> 02:05:55.976
Man may come into full harmony with the formless substance by entertaining a lively and sincere

02:05:55.976 --> 02:05:58.776
gratitude for the blessings it bestows upon him.

02:05:58.776 --> 02:06:03.996
Gratitude unifies the mind of man with the intelligence of substance, so that man's

02:06:03.996 --> 02:06:06.096
thoughts are received by the formless.

02:06:06.676 --> 02:06:11.496
Man can remain upon the creative plane only by uniting himself with the formless intelligence

02:06:11.496 --> 02:06:14.476
through a deep and continuous feeling of gratitude.

02:06:15.256 --> 02:06:19.776
Man must form a clear and definite mental image of the things he wishes to have, to

02:06:19.776 --> 02:06:25.236
do, or to become, and he must hold this mental image in his thoughts while being deeply grateful

02:06:25.236 --> 02:06:28.536
to the Supreme that all he desires are granted to him.

02:06:29.216 --> 02:06:34.056
The man who wishes to get rich must spend his leisure hours in contemplating his vision,

02:06:34.396 --> 02:06:38.396
and in earnest thanksgiving that the reality is being given to him.

02:06:38.836 --> 02:06:43.656
Too much stress cannot be laid on the importance of frequent contemplation of the mental image

02:06:43.656 --> 02:06:47.016
coupled with unwavering faith and devout gratitude.

02:06:47.596 --> 02:06:51.776
This is the process by which the impression is given to the formless and the creative

02:06:51.776 --> 02:06:53.276
forces set in motion.

02:06:54.036 --> 02:06:58.796
The creative energy works through the established channels of natural growth and of the industrial

02:06:58.796 --> 02:06:59.876
and social order.

02:07:00.576 --> 02:07:05.136
All that is included in his mental image will surely be brought to the man who follows the

02:07:05.136 --> 02:07:08.696
instructions given above, and whose faith does not waver.

02:07:09.236 --> 02:07:13.336
What he wants will come to him through the ways of established trade and commerce.

02:07:14.056 --> 02:07:19.076
In order to receive his own when it shall come to him, man must be active, and this

02:07:19.076 --> 02:07:22.476
activity can only consist in more than filling his present place.

02:07:22.476 --> 02:07:27.756
He must keep in mind the purpose to get rich through the realization of his mental image,

02:07:28.156 --> 02:07:33.236
and he must do, every day, all that can be done that day, taking care to do each act

02:07:33.236 --> 02:07:34.476
in a successful manner.

02:07:34.896 --> 02:07:40.136
He must give to every man a use-value in excess of the cash-value he receives, so that each

02:07:40.136 --> 02:07:45.496
transaction makes for more life, and he must so hold the advancing thought that the impression

02:07:45.496 --> 02:07:49.096
of increase will be communicated to all with whom he comes in contact.

02:07:49.736 --> 02:07:55.016
The men and women who practice the foregoing instructions will certainly get rich, and

02:07:55.016 --> 02:08:00.196
the riches they receive will be in exact proportion to the definiteness of their vision, the fixity

02:08:00.196 --> 02:08:04.716
of their purpose, the steadiness of their faith, and the depth of their gratitude.
